Objectives.Description: Eliminate Husks with pistols or SMGs in a 23+ Flannel Falls Venture zone.
Objectives.HudShortDescription: Husks eliminated with pistols or SMGs

Quest:beginnings_seasonal_weapon_04.Description: This is a Clip's Weapons Training Venture Quest. Complete it to earn Venture experience and the next Clip's Weapons Training quest!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate Husks with traps in a 34+ Flannel Falls Venture zone

Quest:beginnings_seasonal_weapon_05.Name: Beginnings_Seasonal_Weapon_05
Quest:beginnings_seasonal_weapon_05.Description: This is a Clip's Weapons Training Venture Quest. Complete it to earn Venture experience and the next Clip's Weapons Training quest!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate Husks with a shotgun in a 46+ Flannel Falls Venture zone.

Quest:beginnings_seasonal_weapon_06.Description: This is a Clip's Weapons Training Venture Quest. Complete it to earn Venture experience and the next Clip's Weapons Training quest!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate Husks with a sniper rifle in a 58+ Flannel Falls Venture zone.
Objectives.HudShortDescription: Husks eliminated with a sniper rifle

Quest:beginnings_seasonal_weapon_07.Name: Beginnings_Seasonal_Weapon_07
Quest:beginnings_seasonal_weapon_07.Description: This is a Clip's Weapons Training Venture Quest. Complete it to earn Venture experience and the next Clip's Weapons Training quest!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate Husks with headshots in a 70+ Flannel Falls Venture zone

Quest:beginnings_seasonal_weapon_08.Name: Beginnings_Seasonal_Weapon_08
Quest:beginnings_seasonal_weapon_08.Description: This is a Clip's Weapons Training Venture Quest. Complete it to earn Venture experience and the next Clip's Weapons Training quest!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate Husks with explosive ammo in a 82+ Flannel Falls Venture zone

Quest:beginnings_seasonal_weapon_09.Name: Beginnings_Seasonal_Weapon_09
Quest:beginnings_seasonal_weapon_09.Description: This is a Clip's Weapons Training Venture Quest. Complete it to earn Venture experience and the next Clip's Weapons Training quest!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate Husks with a shotgun in a 94+ Flannel Falls Venture zone
Eliminate enemies with a pistol or SMG in a 94+ Flannel Falls Venture zone
Objectives.HudShortDescription: Enemies eliminated with a pistol or SMG

Quest:beginnings_seasonal_weapon_10.Description: This is a Clip's Weapons Training Venture Quest. Complete it to earn Venture experience and the next Clip's Weapons Training quest!

Objectives.HudShortDescription: Husks eliminated with a sword, axe, or scythe

Objectives.Description: Eliminate enemies with a club, hardware or spear in a 108+ Flannel Falls Venture zone
Objectives.HudShortDescription: Enemies eliminated with a club, hardware, or spear

Quest:beginnings_seasonal_weapon_11.Name: Beginnings_Seasonal_Weapon_11
Quest:beginnings_seasonal_weapon_11.Description: This is a Clip's Weapons Training Venture Quest. Complete it to earn Venture experience and the next Clip's Weapons Training quest!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate Husks with Hero Abilities in a 124+ Flannel Falls Venture zone.

Quest:beginnings_seasonal_weapon_12.Name: Beginnings_Seasonal_Weapon_12
Quest:beginnings_seasonal_weapon_12.Description: This is a Clip's Weapons Training Venture Quest. Complete it to earn Venture experience!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate Husks with a pickaxe in a 140+ Flannel Falls Venture zone.

Quest:betastormquest_completebetastorms_.Name: BetaStormQuest_CompleteBetaStorms_Repeatable
Quest:betastormquest_completebetastorms_.Description: We're seeing some strange weather patterns in the area. Complete some Beta Storm missions, for Science (and Gold)!

Objectives.Description: Complete 2 Beta Storm missions

Quest:birthday_quest_collectflamingos.Name: Birthday_Quest_CollectFlamingos
Quest:birthday_quest_collectflamingos.Description: What's a party without some great decorations?

Objectives.Description: Collect flamingo lawn ornaments

Quest:birthday_quest_collectice.Name: Birthday_Quest_CollectIce
Quest:birthday_quest_collectice.Description: What better way is there to celebrate summer and beat the heat than kicking back with a cool drink? Go get some ice.

Objectives.Description: Destroy ice machines, freezers, or refrigerators to collect ice

Quest:birthday_quest_collecttowels.Name: Birthday_Quest_CollectTowels
Quest:birthday_quest_collecttowels.Description: There's yet another soggy emergency on the pool deck! Find some towels!

Objectives.Description: Collect pool towels

Quest:birthday_quest_harvestac.Name: Birthday_Quest_HarvestAC
Quest:birthday_quest_harvestac.Description: This summer is a hot one and someone at Homebase broke the air conditioning! Collect air conditioning parts to cool everyone off.

Objectives.Description: Harvest air conditioner units to collect their parts

Quest:birthday_quest_lightfireworks.Name: Birthday_Quest_LightFireworks
Quest:birthday_quest_lightfireworks.Description: Start the celebration and light off them fireworks!

Objectives.Description: Light off fireworks

Quest:birthday_quest_mistmonsters.Name: Birthday_Quest_MistMonsters
Quest:birthday_quest_mistmonsters.Description: Those Mist Monsters always seem to want to crash our parties. Show them the door and take em' out!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate Mist Monsters of any type

Quest:birthday_quest_rescuesurvivors.Name: Birthday_Quest_RescueSurvivors
Quest:birthday_quest_rescuesurvivors.Description: The heat wave is picking up. Bring in survivors so they can cool off and kick it with the rest of Homebase!

Objectives.Description: Rescue survivors
(Hidden) Complete BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_RaySignal
(Hidden) Tertiary Mission
(Hidden) Complete BlockbusterQuest_2018_Landmark_Meteor
(Hidden) Complete BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Magnets Quest
(Hidden) Watch Blockbuster Video

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_killchromehu.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_KillChromeHusky_Repeatable
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_killchromehu.Description:
Now that you have access to a Perk Recombobulator, eliminate as many Chrome Husky Husks as you can to earn PERK-UPs to power it. Note: This is a repeatable Quest.

The Perk Recombobulator feature is available after completing the Plankerton Storm Shield Defense 2 Quest.

Objectives.Description: Eliminate a Chrome Husky in a successful mission

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_killfirehusk.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_KillFireHusks_Repeatable
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_killfirehusk.DisplayName: When Fire Husks Start to Burn
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_killfirehusk.Description:
Now that you have access to a Perk Recombobulator, eliminate as many Fire Husks as you can to earn PERK-UPs to power it. Note: This is a repeatable Quest. Fire Husks can be found in Plankerton or higher areas.

The Perk Recombobulator feature is available after completing the Plankerton Storm Shield Defense 2 Quest.

Objectives.Description: Eliminate 300 Fire Husks in successful missions

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_killminiboss.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_KillMiniBosses_Repeatable
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_killminiboss.Description: Eliminate as many Epic Mini-Bosses as you can, Commander! Note: This is a repeatable Quest.

Objectives.Description: Eliminate an Epic Mini-Boss in a successful Mini-Boss mission

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_killmistmons.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_KillMistMonsters_Repeatable
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_killmistmons.Description:
Now that you have access to a Perk Recombobulator, eliminate as many Mist Monsters as you can to earn PERK-UPs to power it. Note: This is a repeatable Quest.

The Perk Recombobulator feature is available after completing the Plankerton Storm Shield Defense 2 Quest.

Objectives.Description: Eliminate 50 Mist Monsters in successful missions

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_killnaturehu.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_KillNatureHusks_Repeatable
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_killnaturehu.Description:
Now that you have access to a Perk Recombobulator, eliminate as many Nature Husks as you can to earn PERK-UPs to power it. Note: This is a repeatable Quest. Nature Husks can be found in Plankerton or higher areas.

The Perk Recombobulator feature is available after completing the Plankerton Storm Shield Defense 2 Quest.

Objectives.Description: Eliminate 300 Nature Husks in successful missions

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_killwaterhus.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_KillWaterHusks_Repeatable
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_killwaterhus.Description:
Now that you have access to a Perk Recombobulator, eliminate as many Water Husks as you can to earn PERK-UPs to power it. Note: This is a repeatable Quest. Water Husks can be found in Plankerton or higher areas.

The Perk Recombobulator feature is available after completing the Plankerton Storm Shield Defense 2 Quest.

Objectives.Description: Eliminate 300 Water Husks in successful missions

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_landmark_com.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_Landmark_Comet
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_landmark_com.Description: We're closing in on the landing site. Search the zone for the crater, deploy scanning equipment, and get ready to fight!

Objectives.Description: Deploy and Defend Scanners

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_landmark_met.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_Landmark_Meteor
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_landmark_met.Description:
Chrome husks, earthquakes, we’d better destroy the meteorite before it strikes again. Stand by to deploy and defend our Anti-Meteorite Lasers.

Note: this quest cannot be completed until you complete "It came from Space!" quest.

Objectives.Description: Destroy The Meteorite

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_landmark_sui.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_Landmark_Suit
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_landmark_sui.Description: We’re ready to field test Spitfire’s suit. Deploy the suit in a combat setting, and prepare to fight.

Objectives.Description: Test The Suit

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_opencaches_r.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_OpenCaches_Repeatable
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_opencaches_r.Description:
Now that you have access to a Perk Recombobulator, open as many caches as you can to earn PERK-UPs to power it. You can find caches in the world by killing Mini-Bosses or looting valuable treasure chests. Note: This is a repeatable Quest.

The Perk Recombobulator feature is available after completing the Plankerton Storm Shield Defense 2 Quest.

Objectives.Description: Open 10 Caches

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_bar.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Barrels
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_bar.Description: Spitfire is missing, and toxic waste barrels are popping up in unexpected places. Search the barrels and discover the connection.

Objectives.Description: Search Barrels

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_bee.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Bees
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_bee.Description: Some heroes aren't born, they're made. Eliminate Bee Hive husks and collect corrupted beehive pieces for Lok's super experiment.

Objectives.Description: Eliminate Beehive Husks And Collect Corrupted Beehive Pieces.

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_bro.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Broadcasts
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_bro.Description: The TVs around the world are broadcasting ominous messages. We need to investigate - destroy the TVs and collect corrupted receivers to understand what is happening. Something is corrupting the receivers, but it is not the storm. TVs are most often found in Suburban and Urban zones.

Objectives.Description: Collect Television Receivers

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_car.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_CarbonDating
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_car.Description: We should check to see if the chrome husks are from the future. Just to be sure. Collect a sample for carbon dating.

Objectives.Description: Collect Sample

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_chr.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_ChromeHuskData
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_chr.Description: We've got new monsters! Take out Chrome Husks and collect samples for analysis.

Objectives.Description: Collect Chrome Husk Data

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_clo.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Clocks
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_clo.Description: Help Dennis prove the existence of time skips by collecting clock parts. Clocks are most often found in Urban and Suburban zones.

Objectives.Description: Collect Clocks

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_com.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_CometShards
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_com.Description: We should probably investigate that massive explosion. Search the zone for any signs of the meteorite.

Objectives.Description: Collect Meteorite Shards

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_con.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Consoles
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_con.Description: The cure for Spitfire’s illness may be hidden in the Vindertech archives. Help Ray track down audio logs related to Vindertech’s first armored suit prototype. Look for system terminals in Industrial zones.

Objectives.Description: Find Project Tailor Files

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_cow.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Cows
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_cow.DisplayName: I Have No Voice and I Must Moo
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_cow.Description: Lok isn’t ready to lead the way, but he still deserves a voice. Collect farm sounds to give him the voice pack of his dreams.

Objectives.Description: Collect Farm Sounds

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_dep.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_DeployCBots
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_dep.Description: We can’t destroy a meteorite without lasers, and we can’t make lasers without glass, so there’s only one solution. Search for lightning glass by deploying SEE-bots in lightning rich environments.

Objectives.Description: Deploy SEE-bots

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_ear.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Earthquakes
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_ear.Description: Is it just me, or have there been a lot of unexplained earthquakes since the meteorite landed? We should probably look into that. Deploy remote seismographs, and I’ll analyze the data.

Objectives.Description: Deploy Remote Seismographs

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_fan.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Fans
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_fan.Description: Help Ray collect fans to clear the bees from Homebase. Found inside houses and buildings.

Objectives.Description: Collect Fans

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_fly.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Flyers
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_fly.Description: You can't battle a mysterious space rock without a team of super-powered superheroes! Let's let the superhero community know we're recruiting!

Objectives.Description: Launch Flyers

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_jul.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_JulyFourth
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_jul.Description: Celebrate the independence of our Home Base with a display of festive fireworks!

Objectives.Description: Launch Fireworks

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_mag.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Magnets
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_mag.Description: The Cloaked Star might have a solution for the Chrome Husk infestation. Stand by to deploy magnetic snares!

Objectives.Description: Deploy Magnetic Snares

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_mai.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Mailboxes
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_mai.Description: Replies are piling up from Lok's superhero job posting. Search mailboxes to find a true hero.

Objectives.Description: Search Mailboxes

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_mat.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Mattresses
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_mat.Description: We've saved so many survivors we're running out of beds. Search the area for suitable mattresses. Beds are mostly found in Suburban and Urban zones.

Objectives.Description: Collect Mattresses

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_may.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Mayhem
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_may.Description: It looks like there's a new vigilante in town. Follow the path of destruction and search for clues for the vigilante's identity.

Objectives.Description: Follow The Trail Of Destruction

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_por.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_PortaPottys
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_por.Description: Homebase plumbing is crisis waiting to happen. Help Jack collect everything we need to stave off disaster. Look for portable toilets in the Industrial Zones.

Objectives.Description: Collect Neutralizer Fluid

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_ray.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_RaySignal
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_ray.Description: It's time for Lok's reign of terror to come to an end. Deploy searchlights to call Ray back to Homebase.

Objectives.Description: Deploy Lights

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_res.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Rescue
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_res.Description: Whether he wants it or not, The Cloaked Star needs our help. Search the zone, we need to find him before it’s too late!

Objectives.Description: Rescue The Cloaked Star

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_res.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Restaurant
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_res.Description: The Taste Wizard predictive ordering network has been corrupted by the storm. Help Dennis destroy Taste Wizard before it destroys us all. The restaurants are most often found in Urban zones.

Objectives.Description: Upload Dennis’ Order

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_ret.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_RetrieveCBots
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_ret.Description: We need glass to build our lasers. Collect SEE-bots to search for evidence of lightning glass.

Objectives.Description: Collect SEE-bots

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_rub.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Rubber
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_rub.Description: We have the Project Tailor plans! Start collecting the materials we’ll need to build the suit as we listen to the audio logs. The high density rubber can be found in Industrial and Urban zones.

Objectives.Description: Collect High Density Rubber

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_sca.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Scanners
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_sca.Description: Deploy scanners to test Dennis’ theory about a rogue network coming online.

Objectives.Description: Deploy Scanners

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_shi.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_ShielderData
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_shi.Description: If we understood more about Shield Husks, we’d be able to improve the shielding in Spitfire’s suit. Collect Shielder Husk data.

Objectives.Description: Collect Shielder Data

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_tan.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Tankers
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_tan.Description: We almost have everything we need to complete Spitfire’s suit. Collect stainless steel as we sort through the last of the Project Tailor audio logs. This quest requires an Industrial zone.

Objectives.Description: Destroy Tank Trucks To Collect Steel

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_tom.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Tombstones
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_tom.Description: The Cloaked Star has been… smashing gravestones. We should probably look into that.

Objectives.Description: Search Smashed Gravestones

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_toy.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Toys
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_toy.Description: Collect stuffed animals to prepare Dennis for the biggest journey of his life. Toys are most often found in Suburban and Urban zones.

Objectives.Description: Collect Stuffed Animals

Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_tro.Name: BlockbusterQuest_2018_Reactive_Trodes
Quest:blockbusterquest_2018_reactive_tro.Description: It’s time to find out if Raven can be trusted. Search the zone for everything we need to build a lie detector. Look for a hospital, which is most likely to be found in the Urban zone.

Objectives.Description: Collect Testing Equipment

Quest:bot_fetch_quest_a1.Name: Bot_Fetch_Quest_A1
Quest:bot_fetch_quest_a1.Description: With the rest of the Homebase Crew joining the fight, Ray faces a difficult choice.

Objectives.Description: Collect movies

Quest:bot_fetch_quest_a2.Name: Bot_Fetch_Quest_A2
Quest:bot_fetch_quest_a2.Description: Ray's ready to take her first step into battle, but it's not going to be pretty.

Objectives.Description: Deactivate surveillance cameras

Quest:bot_reactivekill_quest_a3.Name: Bot_ReactiveKill_Quest_A3
Quest:bot_reactivekill_quest_a3.Description: Take cover! Ray-Bot is armed, dangerous, and ready for action.

Objectives.Description: Eliminate Husks

Quest:brainstorm_quest_a01_gather.Name: Brainstorm_Quest_A01_Gather
Quest:brainstorm_quest_a01_gather.Description: The Door to Darkness is re-opening. Willow needs your help investigating who or what's behind it!

Objectives.Description: Search the Haunted Hotel for clues

Quest:brainstorm_quest_a02_eliminate.Name: Brainstorm_Quest_A02_Eliminate
Quest:brainstorm_quest_a02_eliminate.Description: Lars leads the team into zombie chicken combat with a spooky story.

Objectives.Description: Eliminate Zombie Chickens in Hexsylvania.

Quest:brainstorm_quest_a03_fetch.Name: Brainstorm_Quest_A03_Fetch
Quest:brainstorm_quest_a03_fetch.Description: After falling into a well, Dennis must come to terms with his greatest fears.

Objectives.Description: Search wells in Hexsylvania and eliminate Takers.

Quest:brainstorm_quest_a04_deliver.Name: Brainstorm_Quest_A04_Deliver
Quest:brainstorm_quest_a04_deliver.Description: Those last stories were child’s play. Sarah’s got a REAL scary story to share.

Objectives.Description: Deliver boxes of loungewear to unsuspecting citizens.

Quest:brainstorm_quest_a05_fetch.Name: Brainstorm_Quest_A05_Fetch
Quest:brainstorm_quest_a05_fetch.Description: Spooky stories can always be improved with a campfire! Hint: Best found in Haunted Forest or Swamp zones. Cannot be completed in the Haunted Hotel.

Objectives.Description: Light 6 Campfires

Quest:brainstorm_quest_a06_destroy.Name: Brainstorm_Quest_A06_Destroy
Quest:brainstorm_quest_a06_destroy.Description: Discover Willow's greatest fear by helping her track down and destroy some ominously named tombstones...

Objectives.Description: Destroy Tombstones

Quest:brainstorm_quest_a07_landmark.Name: Brainstorm_Quest_A07_Landmark
Quest:brainstorm_quest_a07_landmark.Description: Foil Brainstorm's spooky plan by battling the Door to Darkness!

Objectives.Description: Fight through the haunted hotel basement.

Quest:brainstorm_quest_a08_fetch.Name: Brainstorm_Quest_A08_Fetch
Quest:brainstorm_quest_a08_fetch.Description: Refresh Brainstorm’s brine and return him to his normal brain monster state.

Objectives.Description: Gather new Brain Brine from lab equipment.

Quest:cannyvalleyquest_filler_10_d1.Name: CannyValleyQuest_Filler_10_D1
Quest:cannyvalleyquest_filler_10_d1.Description: Commander, continue to fight the good fight! Save the world by completing more missions.

Objectives.Description: Complete 3 Fight Category 3 Storm, Retrieve the Data, or Repair the Shelter missions in a 46+ zone

Quest:cannyvalleyquest_filler_10_d2.Description: Commander, continue to fight the good fight! Save the world by completing more missions.

Visit a motel in a 46+ zone
Visit a gas station in a 46+ zone
Visit a truck stop in a 46+ zone

Search the area for eyewitness accounts of Ayers' reign of terror. Look for old watertowers and windmills. Can be only completed in a desert or Thunder Route 99 zone.

Commander, you may want to consider retiring some of your heroes, personnel, and schematics to make room for new recruits and weapon innovations.

Slotting people and schematics will remove them from action. However, once you complete a collection category, you will receive new rewards! Visit the Armory tab to put an item in your Collection Book.

Quest:elderquest_battlethehorde_1.Name: ElderQuest_BattleTheHorde_1
Quest:elderquest_battlethehorde_1.Description:
Now it's time for you and your team to defend your deployable bases and eradicate the enemy!

Make sure you build weapons, ammo, and traps! You don't have much time or resources!

Once you're ready, access the Control Panel, select Tier 7 or higher difficulty, and let the battle begin!

Objectives.Description: Complete a Tier 7 (or higher) of Operation Block Party

Quest:elderquest_builddeployablebase.Name: ElderQuest_BuildDeployableBase
Quest:elderquest_builddeployablebase.Description:
The husks are plotting a large scale assault, and we need to take them by surprise.

Join up with other Commanders, build a base you can deploy to designated zones, and battle!

Objectives.Description: Build a Deployable Base in Operation Block Party with 10 or more structures

Quest:elderquest_elderunlock.Name: ElderQuest_ElderUnlock
Quest:elderquest_elderunlock.Description:
Commander, your squad has done a great job in Stonewood battling husks and saving survivors. However, Operation Block Party needs your immediate attention! 

To unlock Operation Block Party: 
Select the Skills tab
Select the Operation Block Party skill node
Select purchase to unlock the skill node

Objectives.Description: Unlock Operation Block Party Skill Tree Node

Quest:halloweenquest_clearhuskencampment.Description: The crisp fall air must be emboldening the husks. Apparently, jack o' lanterns weren’t enough for these monsters. Now they’re hoarding candy. Get out there and clear some husk encampments!

Objectives.Description: Clear 6 Husk Encampments in High Threat (or higher) Stonewood
Complete 2 High Threat (or higher) Missions in Stonewood

Quest:halloweenquest_collectpumpkinheads.Name: HalloweenQuest_CollectPumpkinHeads
Quest:halloweenquest_collectpumpkinheads.Description: For every pumpkin husk we smash, two more appear! We need to get to the root of the situation before we’re overrun. Collect any glowing pumpkins you see. We need to do some research.

Objectives.Description: Collect 10 Pumpkin Heads in Stonewood
Complete 2 Low Threat (or higher) Missions in Stonewood

Quest:halloweenquest_craftpumpkinlaunche.Name: HalloweenQuest_CraftPumpkinLauncher
Quest:halloweenquest_craftpumpkinlaunche.Description: It’s a destructive season, Commander. Time to create Pumpkin Warheads. You will need them to create the Jack-O-Launcher schematic. Go to the Vault, select Transform, and then select the Pumpkin Warhead. You will need to consume some items and candy to make them. Once you have created enough Pumpkin Warheads, select Transform and create the Jack-O-Launcher schematic. Once you've crafted the Jack-O-Launcher, go fight the Lobbers!

Objectives.Description: Craft the Jack-O-Launcher
Eliminate 6 Lobbers in Very High Threat Stonewood with a Jack-O-Launcher
Complete 1 Very High Threat Mission in Stonewood

Quest:halloweenquest_findgravestones.Name: HalloweenQuest_FindGravestones
Quest:halloweenquest_findgravestones.Description: As I suspected, these pumpkins are evil. Which gives me an idea. If you can find missing step of the Jack-O-Launcher schematic, you can build the perfect weapon. Try looking somewhere spooky like the suburbs.

Objectives.Description: Search Gravestones for the Epitaph in Stonewood
Complete 3 High Threat (or higher) Missions in Stonewood

Quest:halloweenquest_killpumpkinhusks.Name: HalloweenQuest_KillPumpkinHusks
Quest:halloweenquest_killpumpkinhusks.Description: We’ve got reports of husks wearing costumes… and it’s really, really bad for morale. Sacking our planet was one thing, but getting in the holiday spirit? It’s bumming everyone out. Get out there and smash those pumpkin heads!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate 20 Pumpkin Husks in Stonewood
Complete 2 Missions in Stonewood

Quest:halloweenquest_killvlad.Name: HalloweenQuest_KillVlad
Quest:halloweenquest_killvlad.Description: Find and destroy Storm's recreation of the ancient Hexsylvanian tyrant!  Hint: Cannot be completed in the Haunted Hotel.

Objectives.Description: Eliminate Vlad in a successful mission

Quest:halloweenquest_plankertonmissions.Name: HalloweenQuest_PlankertonMissions
Quest:halloweenquest_plankertonmissions.Description: Now that we've defeated the Lobbers in Stonewood, let's take the fight to the husks in Plankerton.

Objectives.Description: Complete 5 Medium Threat (or higher) Missions in Plankerton

Quest:halloweenquest_savesurvivors.Name: HalloweenQuest_SaveSurvivors
Quest:halloweenquest_savesurvivors.Description: Survivors need us now more than ever, Commander. Let's rescue them. Rumor has it, they have some candy.

Objectives.Description: Save 15 Survivors
Complete 3 Medium Threat (or higher) Missions in Stonewood

Quest:heroquest_blakebeard_blakebeardsst.Name: HeroQuest_Blakebeard_BlakebeardsStash
Quest:heroquest_blakebeard_blakebeardsst.Description: Prepare for plunder! Blakebeard is ready to teach you the secret to finding hidden treasure.

Objectives.Description: Find Treasure Stashes
Acquire a Constructor

Quest:heroquest_constructor_1.Name: HeroQuest_Constructor_1
Quest:heroquest_constructor_1.Description: Your Constructor is almost ready for a mission. Assign your Constructor to your Hero Squad. Then, select your Constructor and select Level Up.

Objectives.Description: Complete a mission as a Constructor in a 3+ zone

Quest:heroquest_constructor_2.Name: HeroQuest_Constructor_2
Quest:heroquest_constructor_2.Description: Commander, let's send your Constructor on more missions. It's time for some more ability training.

Objectives.Description: Activate the Bull Rush Ability
Build a Floor for your B.A.S.E. as a Constructor
Activate B.A.S.E. Ability
Complete a mission as a Constructor in a 3+ zone

Quest:heroquest_constructor_3.Name: HeroQuest_Constructor_3
Quest:heroquest_constructor_3.Description: A Constructor is needed more than ever, Commander. A worker went missing recently in the storm. A Radar Tower needs to be built, so we can find and rescue the worker. Have your Constructor build it and bring that worker home!

Objectives.Description: Build a Radar Tower in a successful mission as a Constructor in a 3+ zone
Objectives.HudShortDescription: Radar Tower built as a Constructor

Quest:heroquest_loadout_constructor_1.Name: HeroQuest_Loadout_Constructor_1
Quest:heroquest_loadout_constructor_1.Description: If we're gonna attract the best Constructors to our cause, we're gonna have to build far and wide.

Objectives.Description: Complete 3 missions as a Constructor in a 52+ zone

Quest:heroquest_loadout_constructor_2.Name: HeroQuest_Loadout_Constructor_2
Quest:heroquest_loadout_constructor_2.Description: Commander, let's send your Constructor on more missions to teach the new folks what constructing's all about.

Objectives.Description: Eliminate 300 Husks in successful missions as a Constructor in 58+ zones

Quest:heroquest_loadout_ninja_1.Name: HeroQuest_Loadout_Ninja_1
Quest:heroquest_loadout_ninja_1.Description: A lone Ninja is dangerous, but TWO Ninjas? Imagine the power! Go find us another Ninja, Commander.

Objectives.Description: Complete 3 missions as a Ninja in a 52+ zone

Quest:heroquest_loadout_ninja_2.Name: HeroQuest_Loadout_Ninja_2
Quest:heroquest_loadout_ninja_2.Description: A Ninja in the hand is worth two in Canny Valley. Or something like that. It's time to recruit another heroic Ninja!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate 300 Husks in successful missions as a Ninja in 58+ zones

Quest:heroquest_loadout_outlander_1.Name: HeroQuest_Loadout_Outlander_1
Quest:heroquest_loadout_outlander_1.Description: Outlanders are out there, waiting in the... out... lands?

Objectives.Description: Complete 3 missions as an Outlander in a 52+ zone

Quest:heroquest_loadout_outlander_2.Name: HeroQuest_Loadout_Outlander_2
Quest:heroquest_loadout_outlander_2.Description: We're going to need to find more Outlanders to keep the materials flowing, Commander!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate 300 Husks in successful missions as an Outlander in 58+ zones

Quest:heroquest_loadout_soldier_1.Name: HeroQuest_Loadout_Soldier_1
Quest:heroquest_loadout_soldier_1.Description: Can you attract new soldiers to our cause, Commander? Show 'em what we're made of!

Objectives.Description: Complete 3 missions as a Soldier in a 52+ zone

Quest:heroquest_loadout_soldier_2.Name: HeroQuest_Loadout_Soldier_2
Quest:heroquest_loadout_soldier_2.Description: There are still worthy soldiers out there, among the husks. Go find them, Commander.

Objectives.Description: Eliminate 300 Husks in successful missions as a Soldier in 58+ zones
Acquire a Ninja

Quest:heroquest_ninja_1.Name: HeroQuest_Ninja_1
Quest:heroquest_ninja_1.Description: A ninja watches from the distance! Demonstrate your superior combat skills to recruit the deadly assassin!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate 20 Husks in successful missions with a Melee Weapon
Objectives.HudShortDescription: Husks eliminated with a Melee Weapon

Quest:heroquest_ninja_2.Name: HeroQuest_Ninja_2
Quest:heroquest_ninja_2.Description: Your Ninja is ready to achieve the next level of enlightenment. Level up your Ninja, and continue your ability training.

Objectives.Description: Activate the Throwing Stars Ability
Activate the Mantis Leap Ability
Complete 3 missions as a Ninja in a 5+ zone
Acquire an Outlander

Quest:heroquest_outlander_1.Name: HeroQuest_Outlander_1
Quest:heroquest_outlander_1.Description: Explore the world to recruit an Outlander.

Objectives.Description: Fully explore a 3+ zone in a successful mission

Quest:heroquest_outlander_2.Name: HeroQuest_Outlander_2
Quest:heroquest_outlander_2.Description: Level up your Outlander, and continue your ability training.

Objectives.Description: Collect an Outlander Fragment and Activate an Outlander Fragment Ability
Complete 3 missions as an Outlander in a 5+ zone

Quest:heroquest_soldier_1.Name: HeroQuest_Soldier_1
Quest:heroquest_soldier_1.Description: Soldier time! Level up your Soldier, arm your Assault Rifle. Eliminate some husks!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate 100 Husks in successful missions with an Assault Rifle as a Soldier
Objectives.HudShortDescription: Husks eliminated with an Assault Rifle as a Soldier

Quest:heroquest_soldier_2.Name: HeroQuest_Soldier_2
Quest:heroquest_soldier_2.Description: Your Soldier can shoot a rifle. But can your Soldier effectively use grenades? Let's find out!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate 10 Husks in successful missions with Frag Grenades

Quest:homebaseonboarding.Name: HomebaseOnboarding
Quest:homebaseonboarding.Description: Quest to track when Onboarding mission has been completed.

Quest:homebaseonboardingafteroutpost.Name: HomebaseOnboardingAfterOutpost
Quest:homebaseonboardingafteroutpost.Description: You've earned a Mini-Llama and enough V-bucks to purchase one Upgrade Llama. Head to the Loot tab and get that loot!

Objectives.Description: Redeem a Mini Llama from the Loot tab
Purchase an Upgrade Llama from the Loot tab
Continue the fight!

Quest:homebaseonboardinggrantschematics.Name: HomebaseOnboardingGrantSchematics
Quest:homebaseonboardinggrantschematics.Description: Quest to track when Homebase Storm Shield Defense 1 has been completed. Once it is completed, grant starting schematics behind the scenes to players.

Objectives.Description: Complete Homebase Storm Shield Defense 1

Quest:homebasequest_completeexpedition.Name: HomebaseQuest_CompleteExpedition
Quest:homebasequest_completeexpedition.Description:
Well done, Commander! You can now send your Heroes on Expeditions. If an Expedition is successful, you receive rewards! Your Heroes will need People and Vehicles to accompany them. Expeditions take time to complete and are not guaranteed to succeed.

Visit the Command tab to assign your Heroes on an Expedition. After an Expedition has been completed, go back to the Expeditions Squads tab and see if it was successful!

Objectives.Description: Complete an Expedition

Quest:homebasequest_researchpurchase.Name: HomebaseQuest_ResearchPurchase
Quest:homebasequest_researchpurchase.Description:
Research allows you to upgrade your technologies. These new technologies cost Research Points. You earn Research Points over time. Collect enough Research Points to purchase the Fortitude Research Node.

To unlock the Fortitude Research Node:
Select the Skills tab
Select Research: Tier 1
Select the Fortitude Research node
Select Purchase to unlock the node

Objectives.Description: Purchase Fortitude Research Node

Quest:homebasequest_slotemtworker.Name: HomebaseQuest_SlotEMTWorker
Quest:homebasequest_slotemtworker.Description:
Well done, Commander! You have unlocked the first EMT Worker slot. Slotting a Survivor in this slot will increase your Homebase Power.

To assign one of your Survivors to your EMT Squad:
Select the Squads tab
Select the Survivor Squads tab
Select EMT Squad
Select the 1st EMT Worker slot
Select a Survivor to slot

Objectives.Description: Assign a Survivor to the 1st EMT Squad slot

Quest:homebasequest_slotfireteamalphawor.Name: HomebaseQuest_SlotFireTeamAlphaWorker
Quest:homebasequest_slotfireteamalphawor.Description:
Well done, Commander! You have unlocked the first Fire Team Alpha Worker slot. Slotting a Survivor in this slot will increase your Homebase Power.

To assign one of your Survivors to your Fire Team Alpha Squad:
Select the Squads tab
Select the Survivor Squads tab
Select Fire Team Alpha
Select the 1st Fire Team Alpha Worker slot
Select a Survivor to slot

Objectives.Description: Assign a Survivor to the 1st Fire Team Alpha slot

Quest:homebasequest_slotmissiondefender.Name: HomebaseQuest_SlotMissionDefender
Quest:homebasequest_slotmissiondefender.Description:
Well done, Commander! You have unlocked the first Mission Defender slot.

To assign one of your Defenders to accompany you on a mission:
Select the Heroes tab
Select the 1st Mission Defender slot
Select a Defender to slot

Objectives.Description: (Hidden) Used for Achievement Purposes

Quest:homebasequest_slotoutpostdefender.Name: HomebaseQuest_SlotOutpostDefender
Quest:homebasequest_slotoutpostdefender.Description:
Congratulations, Commander! You have recruited a Rifleman Defender.

To assign your Defender to your Defender Squad:
Select the Squads tab
Select the Defender Squads tab
Select Stonewood Storm Shield
Select the Rifleman Defender slot
Select your Rifleman Defender to slot

Objectives.Description: (Hidden) Used for Achievement Purposes

Quest:homebasequest_unlockemtworker.Name: HomebaseQuest_UnlockEMTWorker
Quest:homebasequest_unlockemtworker.Description: Quest to track unlock the EMT Worker skill tree node.

Objectives.Description: Unlock EMT Worker Skill Tree Node

Quest:homebasequest_unlockexpeditions.Name: HomebaseQuest_UnlockExpeditions
Quest:homebasequest_unlockexpeditions.Description: Quest to track unlock the Expeditions skill tree node.

Objectives.Description: Unlock Expeditions Skill Tree Node

Quest:homebasequest_unlockfireteamalphaw.Name: HomebaseQuest_UnlockFireTeamAlphaWorker
Quest:homebasequest_unlockfireteamalphaw.Description: Quest to track unlock the Fire Team Alpha Worker skill tree node.

Objectives.Description: Unlock Fire Team Alpha Skill Tree Node

Quest:homebasequest_unlockmissiondefende.Name: HomebaseQuest_UnlockMissionDefender
Quest:homebasequest_unlockmissiondefende.Description:
Defenders can also accompany your heroes on missions, provided that you don't already have a full team of Heroes.

To unlock your first Missions Defender:
Select the Skills tab
Select Skill Tree: Tier 1
Select the Mission Defender skill node
Select Purchase to unlock the skill node

Objectives.Description: Unlock Mission Defender Skill Tree Node

Quest:homebasequest_unlockoutpostdefende.Name: HomebaseQuest_UnlockOutpostDefender
Quest:homebasequest_unlockoutpostdefende.Description:
Commander, we're going to need more help in the next Storm Shield Defense. We can recruit certain survivors to become Defenders.

To unlock your first Storm Shield Defender:
Select the Skills tab
Select Skill Tree: Tier 1
Select the Homebase Defender skill node
Select Purchase to unlock the skill node

Objectives.Description: Unlock Homebase Defender Skill Tree Node

Quest:homebasequest_unlockresearch.Name: HomebaseQuest_UnlockResearch
Quest:homebasequest_unlockresearch.Description: Quest to track unlock the Research skill tree node.

Objectives.Description: Unlock Research Skill Tree Node

Quest:homebasequest_unlocksquads.Name: HomebaseQuest_UnlockSquads
Quest:homebasequest_unlocksquads.Description:
Increase your Homebase Power by assigning Survivors to a Survivor Squad.

To unlock the ability to assign a Survivor to one of your Survivor Squads:
Select the Skills tab
Select Skill Tree: Tier 1
Select the Squads skill node
Select Purchase to unlock the skill node

Objectives.Description: Purchase the Unlock Squads Skill Tree Node

Quest:homebasequest_weakpointvision.Name: HomebaseQuest_WeakPointVision
Quest:homebasequest_weakpointvision.Description:
When harvesting, a "Weak Point" will display as a flash of blue light. Swing for the light and reap the rewards!

To unlock Weakpoint Vision:
Select the Skills tab
Select Skill Tree: Tier 1
Select the Weakpoint Vision skill node
Select Purchase to unlock the skill node

Objectives.Description: Unlock Weakpoint Vision Skill Tree Node

Quest:hordequest_buildbase.Name: HordeQuest_BuildBase
Quest:hordequest_buildbase.Description: You need to set up your Deployable fort before Challenging the Horde! Build at least 10 structures.

Quest:reactivequest_gathercollect_hallow.Name: ReactiveQuest_GatherCollect_Halloween_1
Quest:reactivequest_gathercollect_hallow.Description: Harvest any laboratory equipment you find. Maybe we can learn something from these amateur Hexsylvania scientists

Objectives.Description: Collect 20 notes by harvesting laboratory equipment in successful Hexsylvania missions

Quest:reactivequest_gathercollect_hallow.Name: ReactiveQuest_GatherCollect_Halloween_2
Quest:reactivequest_gathercollect_hallow.Description: Vlad supposedly created a powerful enchanted ore called Vladimantium. We could use some powerful enchanted ores! Collect some for analysis.

Objectives.Description: Collect 25 Vladamantium ingots by harvesting Chandeliers and Candelabras in successful Hexsylvania missions

Quest:reactivequest_gathercollect_hallow.Name: ReactiveQuest_GatherCollect_Halloween_3
Quest:reactivequest_gathercollect_hallow.Description: It wouldn't hurt to have a vampire detection system. Harvest mirrors to collect any mirror fragments.

Objectives.Description: Collect 13 Mirror Fragments by harvesting mirrors in successful Hexsylvania missions

Quest:reactivequest_gathercollect_hallow.Name: ReactiveQuest_GatherCollect_Halloween_4
Quest:reactivequest_gathercollect_hallow.Description: We need to make sure any remaining survivors have a chance to fight back until we return. Start by collecting garlic.

Objectives.Description: Collect 12 Pristine Braids of Garlic by harvesting cupboards, shelves, and shacks in successful Hexsylvania missions

Quest:reactivequest_gathercollect_hallow.Name: ReactiveQuest_GatherCollect_Halloween_5
Quest:reactivequest_gathercollect_hallow.Description: Collect wooden stakes for the survivor care packages.

Objectives.Description: Collect 30 Wooden Stakes by harvesting trees in Hexsylvania, requires successful missions

Quest:reactivequest_gathercollect_hallow.Name: ReactiveQuest_GatherCollect_Halloween_6
Quest:reactivequest_gathercollect_hallow.Description: (temp) gather objects by harvesting "X" in transylvania

Objectives.Description: (temp) Collect "X" by harvesting "Y" in Transylvania, requires successful mission

Quest:reactivequest_gatherfood.Name: ReactiveQuest_GatherFood
Quest:reactivequest_gatherfood.Description: The people demand burgers. Help Dennis set up shop. May require multiple missions.

Objectives.Description: Gather 8 containers of food in successful missions in a 34+ zone

Quest:reactivequest_gatherhydraulic_1.Name: ReactiveQuest_GatherHydraulic_1
Quest:reactivequest_gatherhydraulic_1.Description: So, that cool new hydraulic weapon update everyone’s talking about… It got slightly deleted. But, don’t worry,  if you can collect some hydraulic pistol parts we should be able to recreate a prototype from memory.

Objectives.Description: Collect hydraulic pistol parts by harvesting mechanical objects in successful missions

Quest:reactivequest_gatherhydraulic_2.Name: ReactiveQuest_GatherHydraulic_2
Quest:reactivequest_gatherhydraulic_2.Description: Part of the Hydraulic Weapons update was deleted. If you can collect hydraulic rifle parts we should be able to recreate one of the missing prototypes from memory.

Objectives.Description: Collect hydraulic rifle parts by harvesting mechanical objects in successful missions

Quest:reactivequest_gatherhydraulic_3.Name: ReactiveQuest_GatherHydraulic_3
Quest:reactivequest_gatherhydraulic_3.Description: Part of the Hydraulic Weapons update was deleted. If you can collect hydraulic rifle parts we should be able to recreate one of the missing prototypes from memory.

Objectives.Description: Collect hydraulic sniper parts by harvesting large vehicles in successful missions
Gather 4 pieces of Vindertech experimental code in successful missions in a 5+ zone

Quest:reactivequest_halloween_destroy_1.Name: ReactiveQuest_Halloween_Destroy_1
Quest:reactivequest_halloween_destroy_1.Description: Search the dungeons and catacombs and smash anything evil you see.

Objectives.Description: Destroy 8 Pieces of Dungeon Hardware in successful Hexsylvania missions

Quest:reactivequest_halloween_destroy_10.Name: ReactiveQuest_Halloween_Destroy_10
Quest:reactivequest_halloween_destroy_10.Description: We've got a bat problem. Send those bats a message by destroying any Hexsylvanian bells you find.

Objectives.Description: Destroy 6 Large Bells in successful Hexsylvania missions

Quest:reactivequest_halloween_destroy_2.Name: ReactiveQuest_Halloween_Destroy_2
Quest:reactivequest_halloween_destroy_2.DisplayName: It's a Vlad Vlad Vlad Vlad World
Quest:reactivequest_halloween_destroy_2.Description: There's something creepy going on with those Vlad statues. Let's knock 'em down!

Objectives.Description: Destroy 10 Vlad Statues in successful Hexsylvania missions

Quest:reactivequest_halloween_destroy_3.Name: ReactiveQuest_Halloween_Destroy_3
Quest:reactivequest_halloween_destroy_3.Description: Let's do the survivors a favor and destroy any cages you find in the catacombs. I don't want those husks getting any ideas...

Objectives.Description: Destroy 10 Cages in successful Hexsylvania missions

Quest:reactivequest_halloween_destroy_4.Name: ReactiveQuest_Halloween_Destroy_4
Quest:reactivequest_halloween_destroy_4.Description: I'm getting reports of graves with high levels of storm corruption. So... you know. Take care of that.

Objectives.Description: Destroy 4 Gothic Graves in successful Hexsylvania missions

Quest:reactivequest_halloween_destroy_5.Name: ReactiveQuest_Halloween_Destroy_5
Quest:reactivequest_halloween_destroy_5.Description: We want to keep the storm from finding anything that belonged to Vlad. Start by destroying any thrones you find.

Objectives.Description: Destroy 12 Thrones in successful Hexsylvania missions

Quest:reactivequest_halloween_destroy_6.Name: ReactiveQuest_Halloween_Destroy_6
Quest:reactivequest_halloween_destroy_6.Description: The rickety Hexsylvanian shacks are a deathtrap for survivors. Let's clear as many as we can.

Objectives.Description: Destroy 12 Small Shacks in successful Hexsylvania missions

Quest:reactivequest_halloween_destroy_7.Name: ReactiveQuest_Halloween_Destroy_7
Quest:reactivequest_halloween_destroy_7.Description: I cannot rule out a "Playing Chess with Death Scenario" here, so let's destroy any Chess Sets you find in Hexsylvania.

Objectives.Description: Destroy 8 Chess tables in successful Hexsylvania missions

Quest:reactivequest_halloween_destroy_8.Name: ReactiveQuest_Halloween_Destroy_8
Quest:reactivequest_halloween_destroy_8.Description: We need to keep the bees from teaming up with the husks. Destroy any fancy bee huts you find!

Objectives.Description: Destroy 10 Bee huts in successful Hexsylvania missions

Quest:reactivequest_halloween_destroy_9.Name: ReactiveQuest_Halloween_Destroy_9
Quest:reactivequest_halloween_destroy_9.Description: The signs seem to be directing survivors to the most dangerous places imaginable. We should fix that.

Objectives.Description: Destroy 24 Signs in successful Hexsylvania missions

Quest:reactivequest_halloween_fetch_1.Name: ReactiveQuest_Halloween_Fetch_1

Objectives.Description: Place 15 Gramophones in successful Hexsylvania missions

Quest:reactivequest_halloween_fetch_2.Name: ReactiveQuest_Halloween_Fetch_2
Quest:reactivequest_halloween_fetch_2.Description: Legend has it, the entire historical record of Hexsylvania was burned. Search the grand fireplaces of Hexsylvania for any remnants.

Objectives.Description: Search 10 Grand Fireplaces in successful Hexsylvania missions

Quest:reactivequest_halloween_fetch_3.Name: ReactiveQuest_Halloween_Fetch_3
Quest:reactivequest_halloween_fetch_3.Description: Find Vlad's coffin before the storm does.

Objectives.Description: Search stone coffins for Vlad's burial place in successful Hexsylvania missions

Quest:reactivequest_halloween_fetch_4.Name: ReactiveQuest_Halloween_Fetch_4
Quest:reactivequest_halloween_fetch_4.Description: Search for Vlad's final resting place by deploying SAW-Bots in Haunted Forests.

Objectives.Description: Deploy 5 SAW-Bots in successful Hexsylvania missions

Quest:reactivequest_halloween_fetch_5.Name: ReactiveQuest_Halloween_Fetch_5
Quest:reactivequest_halloween_fetch_5.Description: Distribute survival kits to give remaining survivors a fighting chance!

Objectives.Description: Place 15 Survival Kits in successful Hexsylvania missions

Quest:reactivequest_halloween_fetch_6.Name: ReactiveQuest_Halloween_Fetch_6
Quest:reactivequest_halloween_fetch_6.Description: Deploy SAW-Bot at the Gothic Ruins in Hexsylvania.

Objectives.Description: Deploy the final SAW-Bot at the Gothic Ruins in Hexsylvania
Examine Vlad's coffin

Quest:reactivequest_halloween_fetch_7.Name: ReactiveQuest_Halloween_Fetch_7
Quest:reactivequest_halloween_fetch_7.Description: Even in the shadow of Vlad's storm, there is still light. A kind, talented, and driven artist once lived in this land. Collect the fragments of her composition, and return her music to Hexsylvania.

Objectives.Description: Find 5 fragments of a music piece in successful Hexsylvania missions

Quest:reactivequest_halloween_killcollec.Name: ReactiveQuest_Halloween_KillCollect_PumpkinHusks
Quest:reactivequest_halloween_killcollec.Description: (temp) Collect 40 fallen pumpkins from  Pumpkin Husks in Transylvania

Objectives.Description: (temp) Collect 40 fallen Pumpkins from Pumpkin Husks in Transylvania, requires successful mission

Quest:reactivequest_halloween_killcollec.Name: ReactiveQuest_Halloween_KillCollect_Taker
Quest:reactivequest_halloween_killcollec.DisplayName: Lok's Book of Monsters: Vampire Takers
Quest:reactivequest_halloween_killcollec.Description: Is it just me, or are the takers here a little vampirey? Eliminate some Vampire Takers, and collect samples.

Objectives.Description: Collect 15 data samples from Vampire Takers in successful Hexsylvania missions

Quest:reactivequest_itsatrap.Name: ReactiveQuest_ItsaTrap
Quest:reactivequest_itsatrap.Description: Search for trap building materials. May require multiple missions.

Complete 2 missions in a 5+ zone
Eliminate the Smasher
Collect Husk Data in successful missions in a 5+ zone

Quest:reactivequest_lightninghusks.Name: ReactiveQuest_LightningHusks
Quest:reactivequest_lightninghusks.Description: Collect Lightning Husk samples for Lok.

Objectives.Description: Gather 10 pieces of Lightning monster data in successful missions in a 34+ zone
Complete the Vindertech Research Lab mission

Quest:reactivequest_medicaldata.Name: ReactiveQuest_MedicalData
Quest:reactivequest_medicaldata.Description: Search nearby computers for medical journals. May require multiple missions.

Objectives.Description: Download 4 Medical Records in successful missions in a 9+ zone
Complete 2 missions in a 9+ zone

Quest:reactivequest_medicalsupplies.Name: ReactiveQuest_MedicalSupplies
Quest:reactivequest_medicalsupplies.Description: Collect medical supplies for Dr. Blackwell. May require multiple missions.

Objectives.Description: Find 4 Medical Supplies in successful missions in a 9+ zone

Quest:reactivequest_poisonlobbers.Name: ReactiveQuest_PoisonLobbers
Quest:reactivequest_poisonlobbers.Description: Collect Bee Lobber samples for Lok.

Objectives.Description: Gather 10 pieces of Bee Lobber enemy data in successful missions in a 23+ zone

Quest:reactivequest_pumpkins.Name: ReactiveQuest_Pumpkins
Quest:reactivequest_pumpkins.Description: Pumpkins are trying to rule the world, eat the special ones

Objectives.Description: Eat the pumpkins, what could be more important than this!
Find 5 pieces of broadcasting studio equipment in successful missions in a 23+ zone

Quest:reactivequest_riftdata.Name: ReactiveQuest_RiftData
Quest:reactivequest_riftdata.Description: Deploy SEE-bot to gather data about the Rifts.

Objectives.Description: Gather Rift data and place the 3 scanning devices in successful missions in a 23+ zone

Quest:reactivequest_roadhome.Name: ReactiveQuest_RoadHome
Quest:reactivequest_roadhome.Description: Collect medical supplies for Dr. Blackwell.

Objectives.Description: Gather 4 crates of medical supplies in successful missions in a 34+ zone

Quest:reactivequest_scavenger_1.Name: ReactiveQuest_Scavenger_1
Quest:reactivequest_scavenger_1.Description: Let's make a new weapon! Scavenge some parts from marked dumpsters, often found in City zones

Objectives.Description: Scavenge parts from marked dumpsters in successful missions

Quest:reactivequest_scavenger_2.Name: ReactiveQuest_Scavenger_2
Quest:reactivequest_scavenger_2.Description: We need to scavenge parts for our new weapon. Gather scavenged parts by harvesting junk, often found in Industrial zones

Objectives.Description: Gather scavenged parts by harvesting junk in successful missions

Quest:reactivequest_seebot.Name: ReactiveQuest_SeeBot
Quest:reactivequest_seebot.Description: Deploy SEE-bot to receive the Phophe-SEE.

Objectives.Description: Deploy 5 SeeBots in successful missions in a 40+ zone

Quest:reactivequest_shielders.Name: ReactiveQuest_Shielders
Quest:reactivequest_shielders.DisplayName: Lok’s Book of Monsters: Floating Freaks
Quest:reactivequest_shielders.Description: We’ve got new monsters! They’re small, they fly, and they’re definitely up to something. Collect Shielder samples, and we’ll see what those floating freaks are up to!

Objectives.Description: Gather 20 pieces of Shielder data in successful missions
Gather 5 pieces of Smasher data in successful missions in a 9+ zone

Quest:reactivequest_supplyrun.Name: ReactiveQuest_SupplyRun
Quest:reactivequest_supplyrun.Description: Collect supplies for Lars' next mission. May require multiple missions.

Objectives.Description: Recover 4 Supply Crates in successful missions in a 15+ zone
Complete 2 missions in a 15+ zone

Quest:reactivequest_survivorradios.Name: ReactiveQuest_SurvivorRadios
Quest:reactivequest_survivorradios.Description: Search the zone for new broadcasts.

Objectives.Description: Listen to Survivor radio broadcasts
Gather 5 pieces of Taker data in successful missions in a 15+ zone

Quest:reactivequest_transmitters.Name: ReactiveQuest_Transmitters
Quest:reactivequest_transmitters.Description: We need to boost our transmission strength, search for locators we can use. May require multiple missions.

Objectives.Description: Deploy 3 locators in successful missions (often found in City zones) in a 15+ zone

Quest:reactivequest_trollstash_r1.Name: ReactiveQuest_TrollStash_R1
Quest:reactivequest_trollstash_r1.Description: Whack a Trolls sometimes drop special keys that will open the Epic loot stash chest. Find the key, and then we'll start a treasure hunt!

Objectives.Description: Find the Troll Key in a 15+ zone

Quest:reactivequest_trollstash_r2.Name: ReactiveQuest_TrollStash_R2
Quest:reactivequest_trollstash_r2.Description: Find the Epic Troll Stash. Trolls like to hide in caves, so that's a good place to start looking.

Objectives.Description: Find the Troll Loot Stash in a 15+ zone

Quest:reactivequest_waterhusks.Name: ReactiveQuest_WaterHusks
Quest:reactivequest_waterhusks.Description: Collect Water Husk samples for Lok.

Objectives.Description: Gather 10 pieces of Water monster data in successful missions in a 40+ zone

Quest:s10_explore_quest_a5.Name: S10_Explore_Quest_A5
Quest:s10_explore_quest_a5.Description: Explore parks where versions of Ray may have returned from the future in suburban and urban zones.

Objectives.Description: Search parks in suburban and urban zones

Quest:s10_explore_quest_a8.Name: S10_Explore_Quest_A8
Quest:s10_explore_quest_a8.Description: Explore potential hiding locations for Dennis Jr.

Objectives.Description: Explore a restaurant
Explore a construction site
Explore a park

Quest:s10_fetch_quest_a10.Name: S10_Fetch_Quest_A10
Quest:s10_fetch_quest_a10.Description: Help set up a tribunal for Dark Ray by collecting judge wigs.

Objectives.Description: Collect judge wigs

Quest:s10_fetch_quest_a11.Name: S10_Fetch_Quest_A11
Quest:s10_fetch_quest_a11.Description: Deploy boomboxes to broadcast Dennis Jr.'s messages from the future.

Objectives.Description: Deploy Boombox

Quest:s10_fetch_quest_a12.Name: S10_Fetch_Quest_A12
Quest:s10_fetch_quest_a12.Description: Deploy sensor balloons to help Lars determine if reality is collapsing.

Objectives.Description: Deploy Sensor Balloon

Quest:s10_fetch_quest_a15.Name: S10_Fetch_Quest_A15
Quest:s10_fetch_quest_a15.Description: It's not a time stabilization suit, but the next best thing: deploy Ned Packs while looking for other ways of helping Ned.

Objectives.Description: Deploy Ned Packs

Quest:s10_fetch_quest_a3.Name: S10_Fetch_Quest_A3
Quest:s10_fetch_quest_a3.Description: Search for DNA testing equipment for Dennis Jr. Hint: Best found in urban, suburban, or industrial zones.

Objectives.Description: Find DNA blood testing equipment

Quest:s10_fetch_quest_a4.Name: S10_Fetch_Quest_A4
Quest:s10_fetch_quest_a4.Description: Find boxes of hypnosis equipment to help jog Dennis Jr.'s memory.

Objectives.Description: Find boxes of hypnosis materials

Quest:s10_fetch_quest_b1.Name: S10_Fetch_Quest_B1
Quest:s10_fetch_quest_b1.Description: You broke time! Search the zone for Vindertech Holo-Kiosks to see if we can undo the damage. Note: the holo kiosks might look different depending on the timeline you are currently inhabiting.

Objectives.Description: Find Holo-kiosks

Quest:s10_fetch_quest_b2.Name: S10_Fetch_Quest_B2
Quest:s10_fetch_quest_b2.DisplayName: Coalition of Doomed and Failed Realities
Quest:s10_fetch_quest_b2.Description: Search the zone for non-apocalyptic solutions to repair our broken timeline.

Objectives.Description: Collect Books

Quest:s10_gathercollect_quest_a14.Name: S10_GatherCollect_Quest_A14
Quest:s10_gathercollect_quest_a14.Description: Destroy cabinets and collect canned supplies to prepare Dennis Jr. for his return to his own reality.

Objectives.Description: Destroy cabinets and collect cans of food

Quest:s10_gathercollect_quest_a2.Name: s10_gathercollect_quest_a2
Quest:s10_gathercollect_quest_a2.Description: Destroy coin operated machines and collect coins to test Lars' theory of colliding realities. Hint: Best found in urban, suburban, or industrial zones.

Objectives.Description: Destroy coin operated machines and collect the coins dropped

Quest:s10_gathercollect_quest_a6.Name: s10_gathercollect_quest_a6
Quest:s10_gathercollect_quest_a6.Description: Help Ned escape his time loop by destroying fire trucks, police cars, and ambulances to collect nedkits.

Objectives.Description: Destroy fire trucks, police cars, and ambulances to collect nedkits

Quest:s10_gathercollect_quest_a9.Name: S10_GatherCollect_Quest_A9
Quest:s10_gathercollect_quest_a9.Description: Destroy book cases and collect "Psychology for Dummies" books in suburban or urban zones.

Objectives.Description: Destroy bookcases to collect books

Quest:s10_killcollect_questa7.Name: S10_KillCollect_QuestA7
Quest:s10_killcollect_questa7.Description: Dennis Jr. needs materials to build a stabilization suit. Eliminate Husky Husks or Smashers to collect the needed Dense Violentium.

Objectives.Description: Eliminate Husky Husks or Smashers and gather Dense Violentium

Quest:s10_kill_quest_b3.Name: S10_Kill_Quest_B3
Quest:s10_kill_quest_b3.Description: Fight the husky horde and keep an ear out for Ray's Time Broadcasts.

Objectives.Description: Eliminate Husky Husks

Quest:s10_landmark_quest_a1.Name: S10_Landmark_Quest_A1
Quest:s10_landmark_quest_a1.Description: Gather intel at the site of the meteor impact.

Objectives.Description: Investigate the meteor

Quest:s10_reactivekill_quest_a13.Name: S10_ReactiveKill_Quest_A13
Quest:s10_reactivekill_quest_a13.Description: Eliminate Mist Monsters to avoid a Dark Future.

Objectives.Description: Eliminate Mist Monsters

Quest:s11_custom_quest_f0.Name: S11_Custom_Quest_F0
Quest:s11_custom_quest_f0.Description: The husks have started a war on presents! Protect as many presents as possible and give everyone a happy holiday. Hint: Must be completed in a Protect the Presents mission.

Objectives.Description: Collect presents in a Protect the Presents mission

Quest:s11_destroy_quest_c1.Name: S11_Destroy_Quest_C1
Quest:s11_destroy_quest_c1.Description: Help survive the week at camp by destroying Slasher axes. Must be completed in Shady Acres.

Objectives.Description: Destroy slasher's axes in Shady Acres

Quest:s11_destroy_quest_d4.Name: S11_Destroy_Quest_D4
Quest:s11_destroy_quest_d4.Description: The villagers are agitated by Arrlene and may be assembling a mob. Destroy their boats to slow them down. Hint: Best found in Hexsylvanian swamps. Cannot be completed in the Haunted Hotel.

Objectives.Description: Destroy boats in Hexsylvania

Quest:s11_destroy_quest_e3.Name: S11_Destroy_Quest_E3
Quest:s11_destroy_quest_e3.Description: Legends about the hotel indicate that scary statues in the garden labyrinth may be the source of the hauntings. Investigate... or interrogate the statues. Must be completed during a Survive the Night mission.

Objectives.Description: Destroy scary statues in the garden labyrinth

Quest:s11_destroy_quest_e6.Name: S11_Destroy_Quest_E6
Quest:s11_destroy_quest_e6.Description: Willow insists that the evil gnomes throughout the hotel be destroyed for everyone's safety. Must be completed during a Survive the Night mission.

Objectives.Description: Destroy evil gnomes in the hotel

Quest:s11_destroy_quest_f0.Name: S11_Destroy_Quest_F0
Quest:s11_destroy_quest_f0.Description: Find and destroy Crackshot's favorite decoration in Crackshot's Neighborhood. Hint: Must be completed in a Protect the Presents mission.

Objectives.Description: Destroy Crackshot's favorite decoration

Quest:s11_destroy_quest_h2.Name: S11_Destroy_Quest_H2
Quest:s11_destroy_quest_h2.Description: Jilly is tired of the other toys stealing her spotlight. Destroy as many as you can find!  Hint: Best completed in City or Suburban zones.

Objectives.Description: Destroy toys

Quest:s11_fetch_quest_b1.Name: S11_Fetch_Quest_B1
Quest:s11_fetch_quest_b1.Description: Mysterious trees in Hexsylvania need to be investigated. Could they be signs of a Werewolf? Hint: Cannot be completed in the Haunted Hotel.

Objectives.Description: Search for clawed trees in Hexsylvania

Quest:s11_fetch_quest_b2.Name: S11_Fetch_Quest_B2
Quest:s11_fetch_quest_b2.Description: Set up telescopes to observe and determine the exact moment of the Super Blood moon. Hint: Cannot be completed in the Haunted Hotel.

Objectives.Description: Deploy telescopes in Hexsylvania

Quest:s11_fetch_quest_b4.Name: S11_Fetch_Quest_B4
Quest:s11_fetch_quest_b4.Description: Interview sleeping vampires resting in their coffins to learn more about werewolves in Hexsylvania. Hint: Cannot be completed in the Haunted Hotel.

Objectives.Description: Give flasks to sleeping vampires in coffins

Quest:s11_fetch_quest_b5.Name: S11_Fetch_Quest_B5
Quest:s11_fetch_quest_b5.Description: Help Dire through the Packstravaganza and get more info on the wolfpack's plans. Hint: Cannot be completed in the Haunted Hotel.

Objectives.Description: Deploy receivers in Hexsylvania

Quest:s11_fetch_quest_b7.Name: S11_Fetch_Quest_B7
Quest:s11_fetch_quest_b7.Description: Deploy wolfsbane amulets in Hexsylvania and restore peace to the land... for now. Hint: Cannot be completed in the Haunted Hotel.

Objectives.Description: Deploy wolfsbane amulets

Quest:s11_fetch_quest_c2.Name: S11_Fetch_Quest_C2
Quest:s11_fetch_quest_c2.Description: Raven is ready to help translate old journal clippings from Slashers you can find in the wilderness. Hint: Cannot be completed in the Haunted Hotel.

Objectives.Description: Find journal clippings from Slashers

Quest:s11_fetch_quest_c4.Name: S11_Fetch_Quest_C4
Quest:s11_fetch_quest_c4.Description: Gather backpacks and prepare for the No Lurking Challenge. Hint: Cannot be completed in the Haunted Hotel.

Objectives.Description: Find backpacks for hiking

Quest:s11_fetch_quest_c5.Name: S11_Fetch_Quest_C5
Quest:s11_fetch_quest_c5.Description: Gather paddles for slashers only canoe race. Hint: Cannot be completed in the Haunted Hotel.

Objectives.Description: Find paddles for canoes

Quest:s11_fetch_quest_c6.Name: S11_Fetch_Quest_C6
Quest:s11_fetch_quest_c6.Description: Grab some targets for hatchet throwing practice and attempt to make peace with the Slashers. Hint: Cannot be completed in the Haunted Hotel.

Objectives.Description: Find targets for practice

Quest:s11_fetch_quest_d2.Name: S11_Fetch_Quest_D2
Quest:s11_fetch_quest_d2.DisplayName: Are We Calling it a Monster?
Quest:s11_fetch_quest_d2.Description: Lightning rods are needed for the next step of Penny's plan. Deploy lightning rods in the area. Needs to be completed in Hexsylvania.  Hint: Cannot be completed in the Haunted Hotel.

Objectives.Description: Deploy lightning rods in Hexsylvania

Quest:s11_fetch_quest_d3.Name: S11_Fetch_Quest_D3
Quest:s11_fetch_quest_d3.Description: Find and read the diary entries to learn more about Arrlene. Must be completed in Hexsylvania. Hint: Cannot be completed in the Haunted Hotel.

Objectives.Description: Find Arrlene's diary entries

Quest:s11_fetch_quest_d7.Name: S11_Fetch_Quest_D7
Quest:s11_fetch_quest_d7.Description: Construct a luxury honeymoon RV wagon by salvaging old wagons in Hexsylvania. Hint: Best found in swamps. Cannot be completed in the Haunted Hotel.

Objectives.Description: Gather caravan wagons in Hexsylvania

Quest:s11_fetch_quest_e2.Name: S11_Fetch_Quest_E2
Quest:s11_fetch_quest_e2.Description: Investigate clues to learn more about the hauntings in the hotel. Must be completed during a Survive the Night mission.

Objectives.Description: Investigate clues in the hotel

Quest:s11_fetch_quest_e5.Name: S11_Fetch_Quest_E5
Quest:s11_fetch_quest_e5.Description: It is time to communicate with the "ghost." Set up spirit boards to talk with Lok's imaginary friend. Must be completed during a Survive the Night mission.

Objectives.Description: Deploy spirit boards throughout the hotel

Quest:s11_fetch_quest_e7.Name: S11_Fetch_Quest_E7
Quest:s11_fetch_quest_e7.Description: Gather pages in the hotel which were torn from Willow's diary and discover how to help. Must be completed during a Survive the Night mission.

Objectives.Description: Collect Willow's diary entries

Quest:s11_fetch_quest_f3.Name: S11_Fetch_Quest_F3
Quest:s11_fetch_quest_f3.Description: Crackshot demands the holiday season's hottest toy. Find it, or else! Hint: Best completed in a Protect the Presents mission.

Objectives.Description: Find presents for Crackshot

Quest:s11_fetch_quest_f5.Name: S11_Fetch_Quest_F5
Quest:s11_fetch_quest_f5.Description: Spread holiday cheer by decorating trees in Crackshot's Neighborhood. Hint: Best completed in a Protect the Presents mission.

Objectives.Description: Decorate trees for the holidays

Quest:s11_fetch_quest_f7.Name: S11_Fetch_Quest_F7
Quest:s11_fetch_quest_f7.Description: Celebrate the holidays by blaring music from speakers for all to hear, whether they like it or not. Hint: Best completed in a Protect the Presents mission.

Objectives.Description: Deploy speakers to spread holiday cheer

Quest:s11_fetch_quest_fgift.Name: S11_Fetch_Quest_FGift
Quest:s11_fetch_quest_fgift.Description: Use the mysterious key to unlock Crackshot's secret holiday treasure - a gift to you! Hint: Must be completed in a Protect the Presents mission.

Objectives.Description: Use the key to unlock Crackshot's hidden treasure

Quest:s11_fetch_quest_fkey.Name: S11_Fetch_Quest_FKey
Quest:s11_fetch_quest_fkey.Description: Crackshot has lost the key to his holiday treasure. Hint: Must be completed in a Protect the Presents mission.

Objectives.Description: Find Crackshot's lost key

Quest:s11_fetch_quest_g1.Name: S11_Fetch_Quest_G1
Quest:s11_fetch_quest_g1.Description: Homebase is having trouble sleeping, so it's time to make the best of the situation. Collect coffee makers to help keep the team awake. Hint: Best completed in a City or Suburban zone.

Objectives.Description: Collect coffee makers

Quest:s11_fetch_quest_g3.Name: S11_Fetch_Quest_G3
Quest:s11_fetch_quest_g3.DisplayName: All I Want For Christmas is Boo
Quest:s11_fetch_quest_g3.Description: Dennis wants to make Willow a delicious ghost meal, but needs some help to find what ghosts eat. Hint: Best completed in a City or Suburban zone.

Objectives.Description: Search book piles for ghost cookbooks

Quest:s11_fetch_quest_g7.Name: S11_Fetch_Quest_G7
Quest:s11_fetch_quest_g7.DisplayName: There's No Place Like Van for the Holidays
Quest:s11_fetch_quest_g7.Description: Join Lars and Willow to deliver gifts to the survivors and spread hope and joy to everyone!

Objectives.Description: Deliver gifts to survivors

Quest:s11_fetch_quest_h3.Name: S11_Fetch_Quest_H3
Quest:s11_fetch_quest_h3.Description: Ray has been deposed and exiled from Homebase. She has a plan and she needs beans to pull it off.

Objectives.Description: Collect cans of beans

Quest:s11_fetch_quest_h6.Name: S11_Fetch_Quest_H6
Quest:s11_fetch_quest_h6.Description: Ray is going to help Jilly make amends and there's no better way than breaking bread with those she has wronged, or - in this case - sharing tea.

Objectives.Description: Set up apology tea parties

Quest:s11_gathercollect_quest_b3.Name: S11_GatherCollect_Quest_B3
Quest:s11_gathercollect_quest_b3.Description: Maybe vampires can help us solve our were-problems. Gather flasks from cabinets in Hexsylvania. Hint: Cannot be completed in the Haunted Hotel.

Objectives.Description: Destroy cabinets to collect flasks

Quest:s11_gathercollect_quest_b6.Name: S11_GatherCollect_Quest_B6
Quest:s11_gathercollect_quest_b6.Description: Gather the wolfsbane plant leaves to deter the wolfpack. Hint: Best found in swamps. Cannot be completed in the Haunted Hotel.

Objectives.Description: Destroy and collect wolfsbane plant leaves

Quest:s11_gathercollect_quest_c3.Name: S11_GatherCollect_Quest_C3
Quest:s11_gathercollect_quest_c3.Description: A big camp fire is a great place for spooky stories. Destroy campfires to gather marshmallow sticks. Best completed in Shady Acres.

Objectives.Description: Destroy campfires to gather marshmallow sticks

Quest:s11_gathercollect_quest_d1.Name: S11_GatherCollect_Quest_D1
Quest:s11_gathercollect_quest_d1.Description: Penny needs bags of... things. Gather bags from lab furniture because she pretty much needs it all. Needs to be completed in Hexsylvania.  Hint: Cannot be completed in the Haunted Hotel.

Objectives.Description: Destroy lab furniture to collect bags of things

Quest:s11_gathercollect_quest_d5.Name: S11_GatherCollect_Quest_D5
Quest:s11_gathercollect_quest_d5.Description: Water plants are a vital component to summon monsters. Harvest water plants in the swamps for the Summoning Soup. Hint: Best found in Hexsylvanian swamps. Cannot be completed in the Haunted Hotel.

Objectives.Description: Destroy water plants to collect its flower

Quest:s11_gathercollect_quest_e4.Name: S11_GatherCollect_Quest_E4
Quest:s11_gathercollect_quest_e4.Description: The ghosts haunting the hotel are restless. Investigating where they took their final rest will lead to answers. Gather ghost ectoplasm samples from hotel beds. Must be completed during a Survive the Night mission.

Objectives.Description: Gather ghost ectoplasm samples from hotel beds

Quest:s11_gathercollect_quest_f0.Name: S11_GatherCollect_Quest_F0
Quest:s11_gathercollect_quest_f0.Description: Finding a needle in a haystack may not be as difficult as everyone says it is. Hint: Must be completed in a Protect the Presents mission.

Objectives.Description: Find the needle

Quest:s11_gathercollect_quest_f4.Name: S11_GatherCollect_Quest_F4
Quest:s11_gathercollect_quest_f4.Description: Crackshot has demanded Santa's head. Ray has a different idea. Collect newspapers to create paper-mache. Hint: Best completed in a Protect the Presents mission.

Objectives.Description: Gather papers from newsstands

Quest:s11_gathercollect_quest_f6.Name: S11_GatherCollect_Quest_F6
Quest:s11_gathercollect_quest_f6.Description: It is time for Crackshot to learn his valuable lesson. Collect expired energy drinks to help him become a large-hearted holiday hero. Hint: Best completed in a Protect the Presents mission.

Objectives.Description: Destroy vending machines to gather energy drinks

Quest:s11_gathercollect_quest_g2.Name: S11_GatherCollect_Quest_G2
Quest:s11_gathercollect_quest_g2.Description: To help Willow feel like she's not alone, Ray has decided to create ghost trees. Destroy beds to collect bedsheets. Hint: Best completed in a City or Suburban zone.

Objectives.Description: Gather bedsheets by destroying beds

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_d1_burner.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_D1_Burner
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_d1_burner.Description: When it’s this cold, it’s hard to stay warm! Make sure you’re doing your part to put BluGlo into the Furnace!

Objectives.Description: Deposit 15 BluGlo into the Furnace in a single Frostnite mission

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_d1_construct.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_D1_Construct
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_d1_construct.Description: So you think you got what it takes to build a Frostnite Fort? Not only does it take planning, but speed and precision! You’re under pressure out there, show me you can do it! Place those structures!

Objectives.Description: Place 100 Structures in Frostnite

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_d1_cramp.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_D1_Cramp
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_d1_cramp.Description: Look at all these Krampi! - Or are they Krampuses? Maybe Krampen? - They’re a threat to everything we stand for! Make sure they’re all cleared out!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate all Lone Krampus targets in a single Frostnite Mission

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_d1_ice.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_D1_Ice
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_d1_ice.Description: Come now! Don’t be shy! Let’s 'Break the Ice' and get to know each other better while we’re together, eh? Break the BluGlo out of those ice blocks so we can keep this fire warm.

Objectives.Description: Break out BluGlo from Ice Blocks in Frostnite 7 times.

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_d2_constructor.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_D2_Constructor
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_d2_constructor.Description: Brrr! It’s cold! But that shouldn’t hold you back! You’re frosty for sure! How long can you last out there as a Constructor?

Objectives.Description: Survive for 30 Minutes in a single mission of Frostnite as a Constructor
Objectives.HudShortDescription: 30 Minutes of Frostnite survived as a Constructor

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_d2_ninja.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_D2_Ninja
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_d2_ninja.Description: Brrr! It’s cold! But that shouldn’t hold you back! You’re frosty for sure! How long can you last out there as a Ninja?

Objectives.Description: Survive for 30 Minutes in a single mission of Frostnite as a Ninja
Objectives.HudShortDescription: 30 Minutes of Frostnite survived as a Ninja

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_d2_outlander.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_D2_Outlander
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_d2_outlander.Description: Brrr! It’s cold! But that shouldn’t hold you back! You’re frosty for sure! How long can you last out there as an Outlander?

Objectives.Description: Survive for 30 Minutes in a single mission of Frostnite as an Outlander
Objectives.HudShortDescription: 30 Minutes of Frostnite survived as an Outlander

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_d2_soldier.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_D2_Soldier
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_d2_soldier.Description: Brrr! It’s cold! But that shouldn’t hold you back! You’re frosty for sure! How long can you last out there as a Soldier?

Objectives.Description: Survive for 30 Minutes in a single mission of Frostnite as a Soldier
Objectives.HudShortDescription: 30 Minutes of Frostnite survived as a Soldier

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_deliver_30.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_Deliver_30
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_deliver_30.Description: Gopher! Deliver the BluGlo! Chop Chop! Those dispensers have to make it at least past 30 minutes or my - I mean, Our - supply will dip! Get going!

Objectives.Description: Survive for 30 minutes in a single mission of Special Delivery

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_deliver_45.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_Deliver_45
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_deliver_45.Description: Mail Call! Mail Call! I need this BluGlo delivered to your burner! Stay out there for at least 45 minutes while I redraw supply routes and other jargon-y stuff!

Objectives.Description: Survive for 45 minutes in a single mission of Special Delivery

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_deliver_bluglo.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_Deliver_BluGlo
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_deliver_bluglo.DisplayName: Keep your hands off my BluGlo!
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_deliver_bluglo.Description: They’re after My- ah- Our BluGlo! Don’t let them take it! If they break the dispensers I’ll never have control over the BluGlo! They who control the BluGlo controls the Universe!

Objectives.Description: Complete Wave 11 with all BluGlo dispensers intact.
Objectives.HudShortDescription: Wave 11 completed with all BluGlo dispensers intact

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_deliver_elite.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_Deliver_Elite
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_deliver_elite.Description: This supply line can’t be broken! You gotta make those BluGlo deliveries throughout the night. I’ll make it worth your while! Just don’t let them take my- I mean- our BluGlo!

Objectives.Description: Complete Wave 20 in Special Delivery

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_frosty_30.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_Frosty_30
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_frosty_30.Description: Just listen to the quiet fall of snow; crunchy, isn't it? Makes you wanna go out and frolic among the husks, taking a swing at them every now and then, spring a few traps, you know, the usual! See you in 30?

Objectives.Description: Survive for 30 minutes in a single mission of Frosty Turf

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_frosty_45.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_Frosty_45
