Quest:s11_holdfastquest_frosty_45.Description: Yeah the traps are freezing, and yeah the night is cold. But don’t let that stop you! Survive at least 45 minutes out there and I’ll make it worth your while!

Objectives.Description: Survive for 45 minutes in a single mission of Frosty Turf

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_frosty_elite.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_Frosty_Elite
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_frosty_elite.Description: Ok, so the traps are freezing up, it’s cold outside, and the enemy have us surrounded. Perfect! They have nowhere to run to now!

Objectives.Description: Complete Wave 20 in Frosty Turf

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_frosty_traps.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_Frosty_Traps
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_frosty_traps.Description: What’s that? The traps are freezing up? It’s only -60C outside! They’ll work fine, and I’ll prove it to you! Go eliminate 100 Husks with those traps!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate 100 husks with traps in Frosty Turf

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_legend_15.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_Legend_15
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_legend_15.Description: You only get so many shots, so go. Each time, higher and higher as you chase that status. This is but a stepping stone.

Objectives.Description: Complete Wave 15 in Final Frost

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_legend_30.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_Legend_30
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_legend_30.Description: They say a journey of a thousand miles begins with a single step. That’s how Legends are forged. This is your first step. Last for 30 minutes.

Objectives.Description: Survive for 30 minutes in a single mission of Final Frost

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_legend_45.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_Legend_45
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_legend_45.Description: Folk tales and heroes are hardly the stuff of Legend. But they have the potential to be. Write me a tale to tell, if you can. 45 minutes is all it takes, now go.

Objectives.Description: Survive for 45 minutes in a single mission of Final Frost

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_legend_elite.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_Legend_Elite
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_legend_elite.Description: The longest and darkest night is here. It is the Final Frost. But remember as they say; It is darkest before the dawn. Survive the Final Frost, so we may raise our mugs to you, once you become Legends.

Objectives.Description: Complete Wave 20 in Final Frost

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_merry_30.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_Merry_30
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_merry_30.Description: Got your melee weapon? Good, you’re gonna need it. The husks are everywhere, and the cold has jammed all the guns. It’ll be tough, but I know you can make it at least 30 minutes out there!

Objectives.Description: Survive for 30 minutes in a single mission of Merry Melee

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_merry_45.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_Merry_45
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_merry_45.Description: You made it to 30 minutes? Great! The temperature keeps dropping, so we’re still a no-go on the guns front. Think you can make it to 45 minutes?

Objectives.Description: Survive for 45 minutes in a single mission of Merry Melee

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_merry_craft.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_Merry_Craft
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_merry_craft.Description: The greatest of weapons are forged in the fires of battle, for it is those that aid you the most! Do yourself a favor, and get one! I guarantee it’ll extend your survivability out there!

Objectives.Description: Craft an epic or better melee weapon in Merry Melee
Objectives.HudShortDescription: Epic or better melee weapon crafted

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_merry_elite.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_Merry_Elite
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_merry_elite.Description: How do you feel about dancing? Dancing among a horde of husks with a trusty melee weapon! Make it through the night and there’s a nice prize waiting for you at the end!

Objectives.Description: Complete Wave 20 in Merry Melee

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_repeat_ice.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_Repeat_Ice
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_repeat_ice.Description: Don’t be picky! Well, actually, yes. Be picky, pick that ice! Get the BluGlo out of those Ice Blocks so we can use them!

Objectives.Description: Break out BluGlo from Ice Blocks in Frostnite 3 times in a single mission (Note: This is a repeatable quest)

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_repeat_pathfinde.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_Repeat_Pathfinder
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_repeat_pathfinde.Description: It’s cold, dark, and we have no knowledge of what’s around us. We need a survey of the area so we have a better shot at success.

Objectives.Description: Explore the entire map in a single mission of Frostnite

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_repeat_taste.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_Repeat_Taste
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_repeat_taste.Description: It’s mighty cold outside! It might not be for everyone, but go ahead and spend some time to get used to things. You don’t have to shoot for the moon or anything, just… try it out. It’s ok if you fail, you just gotta get back up and try again!

Objectives.Description: Survive a total of 30 waves in Frostnite (Note: This is a repeatable quest)

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_seasonelite_cram.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_SeasonElite_Cramps
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_seasonelite_cram.Description: They’re out there! The Krampuses! - Or is it Krampi? - And not just tonight! They’re all the way into next week! Or last week! Maybe even now! I can’t take it! They gotta be dealt with! To the last hair!

Objectives.Description: Complete Krampus Krazies
Eliminate 100 Lone Krampus enemies

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_seasonelite_grou.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_SeasonElite_Group
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_seasonelite_grou.Description: In the season of giving, it’s time to give with friends. Make it through the whole Frostnite in a group of one of each class. This will take the best laid plans with the closest of coordination.

Objectives.Description: Complete Wave 20 of Frostnite in a group with one of each class.

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_seasonelite_knig.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_SeasonElite_Knight
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_seasonelite_knig.Description: Finish all of the waves of Frostnite in the most difficult zone! (Non-challenge missions only)

Objectives.Description: Complete Wave 20 of Frostnite in a 128+ Power zone

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_season_burner.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_Season_Burner
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_season_burner.Description: Keep that burner topped off with BluGlo! (Only available in Frostnite)

Objectives.Description: Deposit 200 BluGlo into the Burner in Frostnite

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_season_furnacema.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_Season_FurnaceMaint
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_season_furnacema.Description: The furnace is what’s keeping the storm at bay and baking my cookies! Make sure you keep it lit, otherwise we’re all in trouble!

Objectives.Description: Keep the BluGlo Furnace above 50% for more than 10 Waves

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_season_loot.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_Season_Loot
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_season_loot.Description: Restock our supplies by looting as many hidden chests or safes as you can! (Only available in Frostnite)

Objectives.Description: Loot 40 Chests (or safes) in Frostnite

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_season_misty.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_Season_Misty
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_season_misty.Description: Eliminate as many Mist Monsters as you can. (Only available in Frostnite)

Objectives.Description: Eliminate 50 Mist Monsters in Frostnite

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_season_survive_1.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_Season_Survive_15
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_season_survive_1.Description: The night is upon us! Do whatever it takes to survive 15 minutes in Frostnite!

Objectives.Description: Survive for 15 minutes in a single Frostnite Mission

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_season_survive_3.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_Season_Survive_30
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_season_survive_3.Description: The night is upon us! Do whatever it takes to survive 30 minutes in Frostnite!

Objectives.Description: Survive for 30 minutes in a single Frostnite Mission

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_season_survive_4.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_Season_Survive_45
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_season_survive_4.Description: The night is upon us! Do whatever it takes to survive 45 minutes in Frostnite!

Objectives.Description: Survive for 45 minutes in a single Frostnite Mission

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_season_trapcraft.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_Season_Trapcraft
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_season_trapcraft.Description: Craft 50 traps of Rare or higher rarity (Only available in Frostnite)

Objectives.Description: Craft 50 Rare (or higher) Traps in Frostnite

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_soup_30.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_Soup_30
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_soup_30.Description: You gotta get a taste of it. Stay out there for 30 minutes, and you’ll get something packed with flavor.

Objectives.Description: Survive for 30 minutes in a single mission of Top it Off
Objectives.HudShortDescription: 30 Minutes survived in Top it Off

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_soup_45.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_Soup_45
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_soup_45.Description: Tasty, wasn’t it? There’s always more. Grab a serving, and go share it with some Husks, eh? If you can let it cook for 45 minutes, I can guarantee you a good meal.

Objectives.Description: Survive for 45 minutes in a single mission of Top it Off
Objectives.HudShortDescription: 45 Minutes survived in Top it Off

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_soup_deposit.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_Soup_Deposit
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_soup_deposit.Description: You ever had perpetual stew? The flavor always changes, but technically it’s the same stew, and it never stops cooking. You can’t let it empty out, and you gotta add something new every now and then. Try it with your Furnace, I bet the results will be tasty.

Objectives.Description: Deposit at least one BluGlo every wave for 10 waves in a single mission of Top it Off
Objectives.HudShortDescription: BluGlo deposited once every wave for 10 waves

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_soup_elite.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_Soup_Elite
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_soup_elite.Description: A long night, and an even longer line. Look at all those husks out there. Do you like Gumbo? Maybe some Tomato Bisque? Those don’t take long to cook, not like what I’m cooking up now. Survive all night and you might get a treat.

Objectives.Description: Complete Wave 20 in Top it Off
Objectives.HudShortDescription: Wave 20 Completed in Top it Off

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_superhot_30.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_SuperHot_30
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_superhot_30.Description: The cold’s almost oppressive. Makin’ the embers dim. Tell ya what, I’m gonna put it on full blast. You should be able to make at least 30 minutes with the heat on your back.

Objectives.Description: Survive for 30 minutes in a single mission of Superheated

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_superhot_45.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_SuperHot_45
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_superhot_45.Description: I got the furnace a-blazin. That oughtta keep out the cold. But them darn Husks want the heat too, I bet. They just keep coming. Think you can run on for 45 minutes this time?

Objectives.Description: Survive for 45 minutes in a single mission of Superheated

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_superhot_build.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_SuperHot_Build
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_superhot_build.Description: Cold, innit? So stick close to the furnace and get warm. If you build some walls and a roof; it keeps the heat in. Why don’t you do just that? Staying warm sounds mighty nice.

Objectives.Description: Place 100 Structures in Superheated

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_superhot_elite.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_SuperHot_Elite
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_superhot_elite.Description: Ever hear ‘A Ring Of Fire’? Cuz we got one o’ those now. If you can keep ‘er blazin through the night, we’ll be set for a good ol’ while.

Objectives.Description: Complete Wave 20 in Superheated

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_waves_30.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_Waves_30
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_waves_30.Description: Riding the waves takes practice. You gotta start small, kiddo! You’re gonna crash into them a lot at the start, and that’s ok! Start small, and try surviving for 8 waves out there, ok?

Objectives.Description: Survive for 8 waves in a single mission of New Wave Holiday
Objectives.HudShortDescription: 8 waves survived in New Wave Holiday

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_waves_45.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_Waves_45
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_waves_45.Description: Congrats on making it past 8 waves kiddo! It’s time to dive in deep. Can you make it past 12 waves this time?

Objectives.Description: Survive for 12 waves in a single mission of New Wave Holiday
Objectives.HudShortDescription: 12 waves survived in New Wave Holiday

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_waves_elite.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_Waves_Elite
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_waves_elite.Description: Think you’re ready to ride the waves? It’s a long night, but I believe in you, kiddo! See you on the farside when you make it through the night!

Objectives.Description: Complete Wave 20 in New Wave Holiday
Objectives.HudShortDescription: Wave 20 Completed in New Wave Holiday

Quest:s11_holdfastquest_waves_target.Name: S11_HoldfastQuest_Waves_Target
Quest:s11_holdfastquest_waves_target.Description: Welcome to the New Wave Holiday kiddo! There’s tons of husks out there to use as target practice, take out at least 50 of them with each kind of weapon you have! Go out there and make waves, kid!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate 50 Target Husks with Melee Weapons in the New Wave Holiday
Eliminate 50 Target Husks with Shotgun Weapons in the New Wave Holiday
Eliminate 50 Target Husks with Assault Rifle Weapons in the New Wave Holiday
Objectives.HudShortDescription: Target Husks Eliminated with Assault Rifles

Objectives.Description: Eliminate 50 Target Husks with Pistol Weapons in the New Wave Holiday
Eliminate 50 Target Husks with Sniper Rifle Weapons in the New Wave Holiday
Objectives.HudShortDescription: Target Husks Eliminated with Sniper Rifles

Quest:s11_intro_quest.Name: S11_Intro_Quest
Quest:s11_intro_quest.Description: Thank you for your patience. Complete Homebase Storm Shield Defense 1 to collect your reward!

Objectives.Description: Complete Homebase Storm Shield Defense 1

Quest:s11_killcollect_quest_d6.Name: S11_KillCollect_Quest_D6
Quest:s11_killcollect_quest_d6.Description: Save Arrlene from the husk mob. Take their torches away from them. Must be completed in Hexsylvania. Hint: Cannot be completed in the Haunted Hotel.

Objectives.Description: Eliminate torch-thrower pitchers and gather their torches

Quest:s11_killcollect_quest_g5.Name: S11_KillCollect_Quest_G5
Quest:s11_killcollect_quest_g5.Description: There's another holiday tradition that Homebase would like to try to break Willow out of her funk - mistletoe! The standard variety won't work for ghosts. Eliminate husks to find ghost mistletoe. Hint: Not all husks drop ghost mistletoe.

Objectives.Description: Eliminate husks to find ghost mistletoe

Quest:s11_killcollect_quest_h5.Name: S11_KillCollect_Quest_H5
Quest:s11_killcollect_quest_h5.Description: Sgt. Tank Gatling demands a trial by combat by eliminating Zappers in the area. Eliminate them and collect dense violentium to prove your case.

Objectives.Description: Eliminate Zapper husks and gather dense violentium

Quest:s11_landmark_quest_e1.Name: S11_Landmark_Quest_E1
Quest:s11_landmark_quest_e1.Description: Explore the haunted hotel and deploy sensors to measure the supernatural field.

Objectives.Description: Investigate the haunted hotel

Quest:s11_landmark_quest_e8.Name: S11_Landmark_Quest_E8
Quest:s11_landmark_quest_e8.Description: Discover the underground crypt and deploy the ghost vacuum to stop the true threat in the hotel - the door to darkness!

Objectives.Description: Deploy and defend the ghost vacuum

Quest:s11_landmark_quest_f1.Name: S11_Landmark_Quest_F1
Quest:s11_landmark_quest_f1.Description: Crackshot has been kidnapped! Collect pieces of the ransom note and discover the kidnappers' demands.

Objectives.Description: Investigate Crackshot's kidnapping

Quest:s11_landmark_quest_g6.Name: S11_Landmark_Quest_G6
Quest:s11_landmark_quest_g6.DisplayName: We Wish You a Merry Fright Maze
Quest:s11_landmark_quest_g6.Description: The best gifts are personal. For Willow, that's a giant maze she can haunt.

Objectives.Description: Build a maze for Willow to haunt in Crackshot's Neighborhood

Quest:s11_landmark_quest_h4.Name: S11_Landmark_Quest_H4
Quest:s11_landmark_quest_h4.Description: Ted has been sentenced to die! There must be a lawyer among the survivors who can plead his case.

Objectives.Description: Rescue survivors to find a defense attorney

Quest:s11_protectsurvivor_quest_h1.Name: S11_ProtectSurvivor_Quest_H1
Quest:s11_protectsurvivor_quest_h1.Description: [PH] Homebase picked up a strange transmission. It sounds like someone needs help!

Objectives.Description: [PH] Find and protect the Tinkerer

Quest:s11_reactivefetch_quest_a2.Name: S11_ReactiveFetch_Quest_A2
Quest:s11_reactivefetch_quest_a2.Description: Investigate clues to learn more about the hauntings in the hotel. Must be completed during a Survive the Night mission.

Objectives.Description: Investigate clues in the hotel

Quest:s11_reactivefetch_quest_h7.Name: S11_ReactiveFetch_Quest_H7
Quest:s11_reactivefetch_quest_h7.Description: Ted and his creations are set on reclaiming his creative spark. Find crafting supplies to help: a mannequin head, sewing machine, collection of thread, bolts of cloth, and cans of dye.

Objectives.Description: Collect crafting supplies for Ted
Collect Thread
Collect Bolts of Cloth
Collect Mannequin Head
Collect Dye
Collect Sewing Machine

Quest:s11_reactivekill_quest_c7.Name: S11_ReactiveKill_Quest_C7
Quest:s11_reactivekill_quest_c7.Description: Join forces with the slashers by showing you can think like them. Use bladed weapons to eliminate enemies Hint: Use swords, scythes, or axes. Cannot be completed in the Haunted Hotel.

Objectives.Description: Eliminate enemies using blade weapons

Quest:s11_reactivekill_quest_f0.Name: S11_ReactiveKill_Quest_F0
Quest:s11_reactivekill_quest_f0.Description: Husks continue to make a mockery of the holidays. Crackshot is satisfied with the current spread of holiday fear, but more would make him even more joyful!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate more Santa Husky Husks and Mrs. Claus Lobbers
Objectives.HudShortDescription: Santa Husky Husks and Mrs. Claus Lobbers eliminated

Quest:s11_reactivekill_quest_f2.Name: S11_ReactiveKill_Quest_F2
Quest:s11_reactivekill_quest_f2.Description: Husks have been making a mockery of the season by wearing discourteous costumes. Crackshot demands Santa Husky Husks and Mrs. Claus Lobbers be taught a lesson.

Objectives.Description: Eliminate Santa Husky Husks and Mrs. Claus Lobbers
Objectives.HudShortDescription: Santa Husky Husks and Mrs. Claus Lobbers eliminated

Quest:s11_reactivekill_quest_g4.Name: S11_ReactiveKill_Quest_G4
Quest:s11_reactivekill_quest_g4.Description: Remind Willow of some of her favorite haunts by eliminating Husks with traps.

Objectives.Description: Eliminate enemies with traps

Quest:s11_rescuehero_quest_h1.Name: S11_RescueHero_Quest_H1
Quest:s11_rescuehero_quest_h1.Description: A survivor named Ted is on the run and needs Homebase's help. Find him in the storm and bring him back to safety.

Objectives.Description: Find and rescue Ted

Quest:s12_buildradar_quest_b7.Name: S12_BuildRadar_Quest_B7
Quest:s12_buildradar_quest_b7.Description: Knox wants to try this "Constructor" thing. Help him by building a radar tower.

Objectives.Description: Build a radar tower for Knox.

Quest:s12_collect_quest_b4.Name: S12_Collect_Quest_B4
Quest:s12_collect_quest_b4.Description: Knox and Lars found survivors near the storm. Get out there and rescue them!

Objectives.Description: Rescue survivors found by Knox.

Quest:s12_danceemote_quest_a6.Name: S12_DanceEmote_Quest_A6
Quest:s12_danceemote_quest_a6.Description: Ray wants to convince Homebase that love is worth the risk. The best way to accomplish this is to dance! Hint: Use a dance emote at the marked locations in the area.

Objectives.Description: Dance at marked dance locations

Quest:s12_fetch_quest_a2.Name: S12_Fetch_Quest_A2
Quest:s12_fetch_quest_a2.Description: Ray has convinced Farrah to not destroy Homebase's capacity for love, instead they are going to destroy dance floors.

Objectives.Description: Place devices to destroy dance floors

Quest:s12_fetch_quest_a3.Name: S12_Fetch_Quest_A3
Quest:s12_fetch_quest_a3.Description: Farrah has commissioned Lars to write a song which captures the anti-love spirit. Help by finding boxes of break-up materials to inspire the musician.

Objectives.Description: Find boxes of anti-love memorabilia

Quest:s12_fetch_quest_a4.Name: S12_Fetch_Quest_A4
Quest:s12_fetch_quest_a4.Description: Lars is ready to debut his newest song inspired by the tragic break ups found in the discarded boxes. Deploy speakers in the area to blast the somber tune.

Objectives.Description: Deploy speakers to play Lars' new song

Quest:s12_fetch_quest_a5.Name: S12_Fetch_Quest_A5
Quest:s12_fetch_quest_a5.Description: Major Oswald isn't giving up on his mission. Help spread anti-love propaganda by deploying flyer cannons.

Objectives.Description: Deploy flyer cannons to spread anti-love propaganda

Quest:s12_fetch_quest_b1.Name: S12_Fetch_Quest_B1
Quest:s12_fetch_quest_b1.Description: Many personnel files were lost during the latest husk attack. Help the Director find hard copies of the files by searching old filing cabinets and uncover Knox's past.

Objectives.Description: Search filing cabinets for personnel files on Knox.

Quest:s12_fetch_quest_b5.Name: S12_Fetch_Quest_B5
Quest:s12_fetch_quest_b5.Description: Helping people, not hurting people. Now that the survivors are safe, help Knox gather supplies for them. Basic supplies. Very basic. HINT: Find stacks of toilet paper in bathrooms.

Objectives.Description: Search abandoned shelters and homes for toilet paper.

Quest:s12_gathercollect_quest_a1.Name: S12_GatherCollect_Quest_A1
Quest:s12_gathercollect_quest_a1.Description: Major Oswald has enlisted the help of Farrah to stop the spread of love. Her first suggestion is to deliver disheartening letters to the team of Homebase. Hint: Best found in Urban and Suburban zones.

Objectives.Description: Destroy mailboxes to collect envelopes

Quest:s12_gathercollect_quest_b2.Name: S12_GatherCollect_Quest_B2
Quest:s12_gathercollect_quest_b2.Description: Knox needs parts from vehicles to fix Lars' van. Help by breaking down abandoned vehicles to find what's needed. HINT: Parts best found in City and Suburb zones.

Objectives.Description: Gather vehicle parts by destroying vehicles.

Quest:s12_killcollect_quest_b6.Name: S12_KillCollect_Quest_B6
Quest:s12_killcollect_quest_b6.Description: THERAPYBOT has been asked to evaluate Knox, but the answer keys were stolen by husks. Eliminate Pitcher and Zapper husks and recover the answer booklets!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate Pitcher and Zapper husks to collect answer booklets

Quest:s12_reactivekill_quest_a7.Name: S12_ReactiveKill_Quest_A7
Quest:s12_reactivekill_quest_a7.Description: Love is back! The love lobbers are also out in force. Eliminate as many as you can to prevent heartbreak.

Objectives.Description: Eliminate love lobbers

Quest:s12_reactivekill_quest_b3.Name: S12_ReactiveKill_Quest_B3
Quest:s12_reactivekill_quest_b3.Description: Show Knox what it takes to be a hero. Eliminate Mist Monsters or 'Sploders to show him how its done!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate Mist Monsters and 'Sploders!

Quest:s13_destroy_quest_a2.Name: S13_Destroy_Quest_A2
Quest:s13_destroy_quest_a2.Description: The now thoroughly dead pirate Blakebeard, wants to show the worlds of the living and the dead that he is a villain of the highest caliber. To usher in this new age of dread, destroy Lanterns and plunge the world into darkness!

Objectives.Description: Destroy Lanterns in Scurvy Shoals

Quest:s13_destroy_quest_a4.Name: S13_Destroy_Quest_A4
Quest:s13_destroy_quest_a4.Description: Willow has placed poisoned punch throughout the world to swell Blakebeard's ranks with ghost pirates. Destroy the punch before her diabolical plan can succeed.

Objectives.Description: Destroy Barrels of Poisoned Punch in Scurvy Shoals

Quest:s13_fetch_quest_a3.Name: S13_Fetch_Quest_A3
Quest:s13_fetch_quest_a3.Description: In attempt to show Blakebeard what it really is like in the afterlife, Willow trapped ghosts so they can provide the pirate with accounts of being dead. Find the ghost cages to hear their stories.

Objectives.Description: Collect Ghost Cages in Scurvy Shoals

Quest:s13_fetch_quest_a5.Name: S13_Fetch_Quest_A5
Quest:s13_fetch_quest_a5.Description: Blakebeard's friends wrote sea shanties about the pirate's exploits. Find Boomboxes throughout the land so everyone can hear these catchy tunes.

Objectives.Description: Find Boomboxes in Scurvy Shoals

Quest:s13_fetch_quest_a6.Name: S13_Fetch_Quest_A6
Quest:s13_fetch_quest_a6.Description: What is a legendary ghost pirate without a stash of plundered treasure? Find sacks of doubloons to add to Blakebeard's ill-gotten riches.

Objectives.Description: Collect Stashes of Treasure in Scurvy Shoals

Quest:s13_gathercollect_quest_a10.Name: S13_GatherCollect_Quest_A10
Quest:s13_gathercollect_quest_a10.Description: One of the most basic rules for survival is to find nourishment. Destroy palm trees to collect coconuts to eat.

Objectives.Description: Destroy palm trees and collect coconuts in Scurvy Shoals

Quest:s13_gathercollect_quest_a9.Name: S13_GatherCollect_Quest_A9
Quest:s13_gathercollect_quest_a9.Description: To prove he is hero material, Riggs must find a way to reorient himself when lost in the storm. Destroy runic boulders to find hidden maps and help him find his way.

Objectives.Description: Destroy runic boulders and collect treasure maps in Scurvy Shoals

Quest:s13_killcollect_quest_a7.Name: S13_KillCollect_Quest_A7
Quest:s13_killcollect_quest_a7.Description: The highest honor to bestow on a pirate is being crowned a Pirate King. Eliminate Husky Husks and find a suitable crown for Blakebeard.

Objectives.Description: Eliminate Husky Husks and Collect Crowns in Scurvy Shoals

Quest:s13_killcollect_quest_a8.Name: S13_KillCollect_Quest_A8
Quest:s13_killcollect_quest_a8.DisplayName: Oh That's What It's Good For
Quest:s13_killcollect_quest_a8.Description: Now that Blakebeard is satisfied, Riggs is the one in crisis. To get some perspective, hunt lobbers and collect their telescopes to survey the land.

Objectives.Description: Eliminate Lobbers and Collect Telescopes in Scurvy Shoals

Quest:s13_landmark_quest_a1.Name: S13_Landmark_Quest_A1
Quest:s13_landmark_quest_a1.Description: Homebase is under attack by a mob of pirates! Complete the Yarrr's Return mission in Scurvy Shoals

Objectives.Description: Complete Yarrr's Return mission

Quest:s13_rescuesurvivors_quest_a11.Name: S13_RescueSurvivors_Quest_A11
Quest:s13_rescuesurvivors_quest_a11.Description: Riggs is confident that he is ready for action. Head out into the zone and rescue some survivors!

Objectives.Description: Rescue survivors in Scurvy Shoals

Quest:s9_destroy_quest_a6.Name: S9_Destroy_Quest_A6
Quest:s9_destroy_quest_a6.DisplayName: The Major, the Lok, and the Wardrobes
Quest:s9_destroy_quest_a6.Description: Help Lok overcome his fears by destroying potential monster hiding places.

Objectives.Description: Destroy closets that may harbor monsters in Suburban and Urban zones

Quest:s9_fetch_quest_a1.Name: S9_Fetch_Quest_A1
Quest:s9_fetch_quest_a1.Description: Lok has gone missing. Use his flier cannons to distribute missing posters.

Objectives.Description: Activate the flier cannons

Quest:s9_fetch_quest_a11.Name: S9_Fetch_Quest_A11
Quest:s9_fetch_quest_a11.Description: Help Jess take the easy way out.

Objectives.Description: Collect televisions for Lok in Suburban and Urban zones

Quest:s9_fetch_quest_a13.Name: S9_Fetch_Quest_A13
Quest:s9_fetch_quest_a13.Description: We've found the area from Lok's broadcast. The monster should be nearby.

Objectives.Description: Search the zone for signs of Lok's monster

Quest:s9_fetch_quest_a14.Name: S9_Fetch_Quest_A14
Quest:s9_fetch_quest_a14.Description: Well... Lok was right. We'd better find a way to learn more about his monster encounter.

Objectives.Description: Search the zone for printer paper in Suburban, Urban, and Industrial zones

Quest:s9_fetch_quest_a2.Name: S9_Fetch_Quest_A2
Quest:s9_fetch_quest_a2.Description: Find out who's responsible for Lok's lock out by reviewing security footage.

Objectives.Description: Collect security footage in Suburban and Urban zones

Quest:s9_fetch_quest_a3.Name: S9_Fetch_Quest_A3
Quest:s9_fetch_quest_a3.Description: Search the zone to find Lok's monster.

Objectives.Description: Search the zone for gargoyles

Quest:s9_fetch_quest_a7.Name: S9_Fetch_Quest_A7
Quest:s9_fetch_quest_a7.Description: Dennis has a plan, and it involves dinosaurs - You know what to do.

Objectives.Description: Collect dinosaur toys in Suburban, Urban, and Industrial zones

Quest:s9_fetch_quest_a9.Name: S9_Fetch_Quest_A9
Quest:s9_fetch_quest_a9.Description: Luna's in charge, and that means it's time to relax and play games. Collect arcade games to get the party started.

Objectives.Description: Collect arcade games in Suburban, Urban, and Industrial zones

Quest:s9_fetch_quest_b1.Name: S9_Fetch_Quest_B1
Quest:s9_fetch_quest_b1.Description: Cap'n Azalea Clark has been spotted at Homebase. It's time to binge watch Beyond The Stellar Horizon.

Objectives.Description: Collect episodes of Beyond The Stellar Horizon

Quest:s9_fetch_quest_b10.Name: S9_Fetch_Quest_B10
Quest:s9_fetch_quest_b10.Description: Every film production has a troll problem or two. Deploy anti-troll vacuums and take back what's ours.

Objectives.Description: Deploy troll vacuums over dormant troll dens

Quest:s9_fetch_quest_b11.Name: S9_Fetch_Quest_B11
Quest:s9_fetch_quest_b11.Description: ED-EE is in space and we have no time to recast. Deploy antennas to record his dialogue from orbit.

Objectives.Description: Deploy communication antennas

Quest:s9_fetch_quest_b13.Name: S9_Fetch_Quest_B13
Quest:s9_fetch_quest_b13.Description: The movie is a disaster! Collect mushy tomatoes before they can be thrown in our faces!

Objectives.Description: Collect mushy tomatoes

Quest:s9_fetch_quest_b14.Name: S9_Fetch_Quest_B14
Quest:s9_fetch_quest_b14.Description: We may need to provide some escape routes from the premiere. Collect red carpets.

Objectives.Description: Gather red carpets

Quest:s9_fetch_quest_b15.Name: S9_Fetch_Quest_B15
Quest:s9_fetch_quest_b15.Description: ED-EE is coming home. Deploy pillows to give him a safe landing.

Objectives.Description: Deploy emergency landing pillows

Quest:s9_fetch_quest_b3.Name: S9_Fetch_Quest_B3
Quest:s9_fetch_quest_b3.Description: Pre-production is a go! Find cameras and prepare for filming.

Objectives.Description: Search the zone for cameras

Quest:s9_fetch_quest_b6.Name: S9_Fetch_Quest_B6
Quest:s9_fetch_quest_b6.Description: Lure Ken back into the acting game by tracking down his iconic catchphrase.

Objectives.Description: Search the zone for Ken's iconic catchphrase

Quest:s9_fetch_quest_b7.Name: S9_Fetch_Quest_B7
Quest:s9_fetch_quest_b7.Description: Script pages are coming in! Track down the best scenes you can find.

Objectives.Description: Collect script pages

Quest:s9_fetch_quest_b9.Name: S9_Fetch_Quest_B9
Quest:s9_fetch_quest_b9.Description: Okay, the script is not great. We're gonna need some very special effects. Collect rocket parts.

Objectives.Description: Search the zone for rocket parts in Industrial zones

Quest:s9_gathercollect_quest_a12.Name: S9_GatherCollect_Quest_A12
Quest:s9_gathercollect_quest_a12.Description: Find books to pinpoint the location of Lok's television projection.

Objectives.Description: Destroy bookcases to collect books in Suburban and Urban zones

Quest:s9_gathercollect_quest_a15.Name: S9_GatherCollect_Quest_A15
Quest:s9_gathercollect_quest_a15.Description: Is this monster encounter a stand alone feature? A trilogy? A prequel? Dennis will decide...

Objectives.Description: Collect video editing software in Urban zones

Quest:s9_gathercollect_quest_a4.Name: S9_GatherCollect_Quest_A4
Quest:s9_gathercollect_quest_a4.Description: Help Dennis prepare for open-bot surgery by collecting parts for a post surgery incubation oven.

Objectives.Description: Destroy ovens to collect heating elements in Suburban zones

Quest:s9_gathercollect_quest_b5.Name: S9_GatherCollect_Quest_B5
Quest:s9_gathercollect_quest_b5.Description: Help Azalea find everything she needs to rebuild ED-EE.

Objectives.Description: Collect ED-EE parts in Industrial zones

Quest:s9_gathercollect_quest_b8.Name: S9_GatherCollect_Quest_B8
Quest:s9_gathercollect_quest_b8.Description: Time to see what our writers have come up with. It's probably fine.

Objectives.Description: Gather table parts

Quest:s9_gather_quest_a8.Name: S9_Gather_Quest_A8
Quest:s9_gather_quest_a8.Description: Help Dennis test out his latest invention.

Objectives.Description: Collect teddy bears in Suburban zones
(Hidden) Watch S9 Video

Quest:s9_killcollect_quest_a10.Name: S9_KillCollect_Quest_A10
Quest:s9_killcollect_quest_a10.Description: The beast must feed! Help Din.0 feast on mist monster samples.

Objectives.Description: Gather mist monster samples

Quest:s9_killcollect_quest_a5.Name: S9_KillCollect_Quest_A5
Quest:s9_killcollect_quest_a5.Description: Husklings have raided the Homebase gold supply. Take 'em out and return the missing rings.

Objectives.Description: Take out husklings and collect golden rings

Quest:s9_killcollect_quest_b4.Name: S9_KillCollect_Quest_B4
Quest:s9_killcollect_quest_b4.Description: The casting office has been raided by husks. Get those headshots back!

Objectives.Description: Take out the husks and collect the missing headshots
Re-shoot key scenes with CG-Bot

Quest:s9_landmark_quest_b2.Name: S9_Landmark_Quest_B2
Quest:s9_landmark_quest_b2.Description: The Beyond the Stellar Horizon soundstage has been found. Explore the set!

Objectives.Description: Search the Beyond the Stellar Horizon soundstage

Quest:scavengerquest_completeexpeditions.Name: ScavengerQuest_CompleteExpeditions
Quest:scavengerquest_completeexpeditions.Description:
Well done, Commander! You can now send your Heroes on Expeditions. If an Expedition is successful, you receive rewards! Your Heroes will need People and Vehicles to accompany them. Expeditions take time to complete and are not guaranteed to succeed.

Visit the Command tab to assign your Heroes on an Expedition.
After an Expedition has been completed, go back to the Expeditions Squads tab and see if it was successful!

Objectives.Description: Successfully complete 5 Expeditions

Quest:scavengerquest_completestormzones.Name: ScavengerQuest_CompleteStormZones
Quest:scavengerquest_completestormzones.Description: These storms are relentless and spreading! Look for purple turbulance on the map! Complete some missions in those hexes.

Objectives.Description: Complete 2 Mutant Storm missions

Quest:scavengerquest_evolve_scavenger.Name: ScavengerQuest_Evolve_Scavenger
Quest:scavengerquest_evolve_scavenger.Description: Visit the Armory tab to evolve a Scavenger Weapon of your choice. Evolved Weapons are more powerful and may require rare crafting ingredients.

Objectives.Description: Evolve a Scavenger Weapon by 1 Star

Quest:scavengerquest_killhusks_1.Name: ScavengerQuest_KillHusks_1
Quest:scavengerquest_killhusks_1.Description: Put your Scavenger Weapons to good use. Team up with other Commanders and rid the world of storm creeps!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate 500 Husks with a Scavenger Weapon in successful missions in a 5+ zone

Quest:scavengerquest_killhusks_10.Name: ScavengerQuest_KillHusks_10
Quest:scavengerquest_killhusks_10.Description: Put your Scavenger Weapons to good use. Team up with other Commanders and rid the world of storm creeps!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate 1500 Husks with a Scavenger Weapon in successful missions in a 52+ zone

Quest:scavengerquest_killhusks_2.Name: ScavengerQuest_KillHusks_2
Quest:scavengerquest_killhusks_2.Description: Put your Scavenger Weapons to good use. Team up with other Commanders and rid the world of storm creeps!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate 500 Husks with a Scavenger Weapon in successful missions in a 9+ zone

Quest:scavengerquest_killhusks_3.Name: ScavengerQuest_KillHusks_3
Quest:scavengerquest_killhusks_3.Description: Put your Scavenger Weapons to good use. Team up with other Commanders and rid the world of storm creeps!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate 750 Husks with a Scavenger Weapon in successful missions in a 15+ zone

Quest:scavengerquest_killhusks_4.Name: ScavengerQuest_KillHusks_4
Quest:scavengerquest_killhusks_4.Description: Put your Scavenger Weapons to good use. Team up with other Commanders and rid the world of storm creeps!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate 750 Husks with a Scavenger Weapon in successful missions in a 19+ zone

Quest:scavengerquest_killhusks_5.Name: ScavengerQuest_KillHusks_5
Quest:scavengerquest_killhusks_5.Description: Put your Scavenger Weapons to good use. Team up with other Commanders and rid the world of storm creeps!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate 1000 Husks with a Scavenger Weapon in successful missions in a 23+ zone

Quest:scavengerquest_killhusks_6.Name: ScavengerQuest_KillHusks_6
Quest:scavengerquest_killhusks_6.Description: Put your Scavenger Weapons to good use. Team up with other Commanders and rid the world of storm creeps!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate 1000 Husks with a Scavenger Weapon in successful missions in a 28+ zone

Quest:scavengerquest_killhusks_7.Name: ScavengerQuest_KillHusks_7
Quest:scavengerquest_killhusks_7.Description: Put your Scavenger Weapons to good use. Team up with other Commanders and rid the world of storm creeps!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate 1250 Husks with a Scavenger Weapon in successful missions in a 34+ zone

Quest:scavengerquest_killhusks_8.Name: ScavengerQuest_KillHusks_8
Quest:scavengerquest_killhusks_8.Description: Put your Scavenger Weapons to good use. Team up with other Commanders and rid the world of storm creeps!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate 1250 Husks with a Scavenger Weapon in successful missions in a 40+ zone

Quest:scavengerquest_killhusks_9.Name: ScavengerQuest_KillHusks_9
Quest:scavengerquest_killhusks_9.Description: Put your Scavenger Weapons to good use. Team up with other Commanders and rid the world of storm creeps!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate 1500 Husks with a Scavenger Weapon in successful missions in a 46+ zone

Quest:scavengerquest_levelup_collection_.Name: ScavengerQuest_LevelUp_Collection_1
Quest:scavengerquest_levelup_collection_.Description:
Commander, you may want to consider retiring more of your heroes, personnel, and schematics to your Collection Book. If you can level up your Collection Book to 30, you will receive additional scavenger rewards!

Remember, slotting people and schematics will remove them from action. However, once you complete a collection category, you will receive new rewards! Visit the Armory tab to level up your Collection Book.

Objectives.Description: Level Up Your Collection Book to 30

Quest:scavengerquest_levelup_collection_.Name: ScavengerQuest_LevelUp_Collection_2
Quest:scavengerquest_levelup_collection_.Description:
Commander, you may want to consider retiring more of your heroes, personnel, and schematics to your Collection Book. If you can level up your Collection Book to 50, you will receive additional scavenger rewards!

Remember, slotting people and schematics will remove them from action. However, once you complete a collection category, you will receive new rewards! Visit the Armory tab to level up your Collection Book.

Objectives.Description: Level Up Your Collection Book to 50

Quest:scavengerquest_levelup_scavenger.Name: ScavengerQuest_LevelUp_Scavenger
Quest:scavengerquest_levelup_scavenger.Description: Visit the Armory tab to level up a Scavenger Weapon of your choice.

Objectives.Description: Level Up a Scavenger Weapon

Quest:scavengerquest_missionalert_constr.Name: ScavengerQuest_MissionAlert_Constructor
Quest:scavengerquest_missionalert_constr.Description: Calling all Constructors! Your building skills are needed. Complete missions with the clock icon for additional rewards.

Objectives.Description: Complete 10 Mission Alerts as a Constructor

Quest:scavengerquest_missionalert_ninja.Name: ScavengerQuest_MissionAlert_Ninja
Quest:scavengerquest_missionalert_ninja.Description: Calling all Ninjas! Your martial arts are needed. Complete missions with the clock icon for additional rewards.

Objectives.Description: Complete 10 Mission Alerts as a Ninja

Quest:scavengerquest_missionalert_outlan.Name: ScavengerQuest_MissionAlert_Outlander
Quest:scavengerquest_missionalert_outlan.Description: Calling all Outlanders! Your exploration skills are needed. Complete missions with the clock icon for additional rewards.

Objectives.Description: Complete 10 Mission Alerts as an Outlander

Quest:scavengerquest_missionalert_soldie.Name: ScavengerQuest_MissionAlert_Soldier
Quest:scavengerquest_missionalert_soldie.Description: Calling all Soldiers! Your combat skills are needed. Complete missions with the clock icon for additional rewards.

Objectives.Description: Complete 10 Mission Alerts as a Soldier

Quest:scavengerquest_purchasellama.Name: ScavengerQuest_PurchaseLlama
Quest:scavengerquest_purchasellama.Description: Scrounge up and save! Earn your very own Scavenger Llama by successfully completing Expeditions and Limited Time Event Quests.

Objectives.Description: Purchase a Scavenger Llama from the Loot tab

Quest:springquest_2018_build_trojan_bunn.Name: SpringQuest_2018_Build_Trojan_Bunny
Quest:springquest_2018_build_trojan_bunn.Description: Whenever we celebrate, the storm attacks. It's time to turn the tables with some hoppin' adorable mayhem!

Objectives.Description: Build a Trojan Bunny

Quest:springquest_2018_complete_bumpeddi.Name: SpringQuest_2018_Complete_BumpedDifficulty
Quest:springquest_2018_complete_bumpeddi.Description: When you locate the primary objective, look for a difficulty pylon nearby. Interact with the pylon and add BluGlo to increase the difficulty. You can increase the difficulty more than once, but it is not required.

Objectives.Description: Complete 2 Enhanced Difficulty Missions

Quest:springquest_2018_complete_firework.Name: SpringQuest_2018_Complete_FireworkClusters
Quest:springquest_2018_complete_firework.Description: Protect and launch a Mega-Llamacracker to light up the night sky with style.

Objectives.Description: Launch 2 Firework Clusters Secondaries

Quest:springquest_2018_evolvedragonweapo.Name: SpringQuest_2018_EvolveDragonWeapon
Quest:springquest_2018_evolvedragonweapo.Description: Visit the Armory tab to evolve a Dragon Weapon of your choice.

Objectives.Description: Evolve a Dragon Weapon by 1 Star

Quest:springquest_2018_killhusksdragonwe.Name: SpringQuest_2018_KillHusksDragonWeapon
Quest:springquest_2018_killhusksdragonwe.Description: Put your Dragon Weapons to good use. Team up with other Commanders and rid the world of these creeps!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate 886 Husks with a Dragon Weapon in successful missions

Quest:springquest_2018_killhusksmelee.Name: SpringQuest_2018_KillHusksMelee
Quest:springquest_2018_killhusksmelee.Description: Break out a melee weapon and show Val how it's done.

Objectives.Description: Eliminate 50 husks with a melee weapon in successful missions

Quest:springquest_2018_killmistmonstersd.Name: SpringQuest_2018_KillMistMonstersDragonWeapon
Quest:springquest_2018_killmistmonstersd.Description: Unleash the dragon and defeat 38 mist monsters with your favorite Dragon Weapon.

Objectives.Description: Eliminate 38 Mist Monsters with a Dragon Weapon in successful missions

Quest:springquest_2018_reactive_cctv_cam.Name: SpringQuest_2018_Reactive_CCTV_Cameras
Quest:springquest_2018_reactive_cctv_cam.Description: Rumors of the Dreaded Clusterhusk might just be true. Search for footage of the rampaging trio of deadly husks.

Objectives.Description: Access 6 CCTV cameras

Quest:springquest_2018_reactive_clothing.Name: SpringQuest_2018_Reactive_Clothing
Quest:springquest_2018_reactive_clothing.Description: Collect tactical clothing for Val. Destroy clothing racks and closets found in urban and suburban zones.

Objectives.Description: Gather tactical clothing

Quest:springquest_2018_reactive_egghunt.Name: SpringQuest_2018_Reactive_EggHunt
Quest:springquest_2018_reactive_egghunt.Description: Help Ray take on her most challenging case yet.

Objectives.Description: Find 9 Easter Eggs

Quest:springquest_2018_reactive_firework.Name: SpringQuest_2018_Reactive_Fireworks
Quest:springquest_2018_reactive_firework.Description: Stock up on luck by launching fireworks and collecting red envelopes.

Objectives.Description: Deploy small fireworks

Quest:springquest_2018_reactive_firework.Name: SpringQuest_2018_Reactive_Fireworks_Repeatable
Quest:springquest_2018_reactive_firework.DisplayName: Things That Go Bang In The Night
Quest:springquest_2018_reactive_firework.Description: Stay lucky! Launch fireworks and collect those envelopes. Note: This is a repeatable Quest.

Objectives.Description: Deploy small fireworks and gather red envelopes

Quest:springquest_2018_reactive_fountain.Name: SpringQuest_2018_Reactive_Fountains
Quest:springquest_2018_reactive_fountain.Description: We need all the luck we can get. The coins thrown into the fountains should have some residual luck in them. Smash the fountains and collect those lucky coins. Most often found in urban and suburban zones.

Objectives.Description: Destroy fountains to collect lucky coins.

Quest:springquest_2018_reactive_garden_g.Name: SpringQuest_2018_Reactive_Garden_Gnomes
Quest:springquest_2018_reactive_garden_g.Description: To banish our storm leprechaun, we’ll need to learn his name. Search for his signature on green painted gnomes.

Objectives.Description: Find 5 Green Garden Gnomes

Quest:springquest_2018_reactive_gymstuff.Name: SpringQuest_2018_Reactive_GymStuff
Quest:springquest_2018_reactive_gymstuff.Description: Collect gym equipment for Val. Found in urban and suburban zones.

Objectives.Description: Gather 5 pieces of training equipment

Quest:springquest_2018_reactive_huntmini.Name: SpringQuest_2018_Reactive_HuntMiniboss_Finale
Quest:springquest_2018_reactive_huntmini.Description: A deadly cluster of dangerous husks is on the loose! Team up and take out all three.

Objectives.Description: Eliminate the dreaded clusterhusk!

Quest:springquest_2018_reactive_killcoll.Name: SpringQuest_2018_Reactive_KillCollect_Clovers
Quest:springquest_2018_reactive_killcoll.Description: Do the husks seem luckier than usual? Take 'em out and look for clues.

Objectives.Description: Eliminate & Collect: 50 lucky clovers

Quest:springquest_2018_reactive_lanterns.Name: SpringQuest_2018_Reactive_Lanterns
Quest:springquest_2018_reactive_lanterns.Description: Place red lanterns for fortune and luck.

Objectives.Description: Place 8 lanterns

Quest:springquest_2018_reactive_leprecha.Name: SpringQuest_2018_Reactive_Leprechaun_Traps
Quest:springquest_2018_reactive_leprecha.Description: To trap a leprechaun, you're going to need some tasty treats. Bait traps with leprechaun endorsed snacks.

Objectives.Description: Deploy 5 Leprechaun Traps

Quest:springquest_2018_reactive_location.Name: SpringQuest_2018_Reactive_LocationDiscovery_Pub
Quest:springquest_2018_reactive_location.DisplayName: You Don't Have To Go Home...
Quest:springquest_2018_reactive_location.Description: Search for a pub to learn the Leprechaun's true name. Pubs are most often found in downtown city areas.

Objectives.Description: Visit one pub

Quest:springquest_2018_reactive_potsofgo.Name: SpringQuest_2018_Reactive_PotsOfGold
Quest:springquest_2018_reactive_potsofgo.Description: Commander, there's free gold EVERYWHERE! Oh, and on an unrelated note, we have reports there's a new storm hazard luring people into dangerous situations. So get out there and don't come back until we're rich!

Objectives.Description: Search the zone for Storm Gold

Quest:springquest_2018_reactive_quotes.Name: SpringQuest_2018_Reactive_Quotes
Quest:springquest_2018_reactive_quotes.Description: Prepare a speech for Val's graduation.

Objectives.Description: Search 5 book stacks

Quest:springquest_2018_reactive_rescueva.Name: SpringQuest_2018_Reactive_RescueVal
Quest:springquest_2018_reactive_rescueva.Description: Find and defend a stranded survivor.

Objectives.Description: Find & Defend Val

Quest:springquest_2018_reactive_tents.Name: SpringQuest_2018_Reactive_Tents
Quest:springquest_2018_reactive_tents.Description: Help Val find the rest of her team.

Objectives.Description: Search 5 tents for Val's team

Quest:springquest_2018_reactive_vhs.Name: SpringQuest_2018_Reactive_VHS
Quest:springquest_2018_reactive_vhs.Description: Find the perfect film to help Val power through her training.

Objectives.Description: Gather 8 VHS tapes

Quest:starlightquest_complete_all.Name: StarlightQuest_Complete_All
Quest:starlightquest_complete_all.Description: Complete the following Dungeons: The Crypts, Inferno, The Grotto, and The Labyrinth.

Objectives.Description: Complete the Crypts Dungeon.
Complete the Inferno Dungeon.
Complete the Grotto Dungeon.
Complete the Labyrinth Dungeon.

Quest:starlightquest_complete_all_hard.Name: StarlightQuest_Complete_All_Hard
Quest:starlightquest_complete_all_hard.Description: Complete the following Dungeons at the most challenging level: The Crypts, Inferno, The Grotto, and The Labyrinth.

Objectives.Description: Complete the Crypts Dungeon in a 140+ zone.
Complete the Inferno Dungeon in a 140+ zone.
Complete the Grotto Dungeon in a 140+ zone.
Complete the Labyrinth Dungeon in a 140+ zone.

Quest:starlightquest_complete_d1_a.Name: StarlightQuest_Complete_D1_A
Quest:starlightquest_complete_d1_a.Description: The Crypts beckon you to enter and defeat its master! Complete a mission in the Crypts Dungeon to gain access to The Inferno and The Lab!

Objectives.Description: Complete a mission in the Crypts Dungeon.

Quest:starlightquest_complete_d1_b.Name: StarlightQuest_Complete_D1_B
Quest:starlightquest_complete_d1_b.Description: The Crypts are certainly a spooky place, but not too spooky for you! Complete two more missions in the Crypts Dungeon.

Objectives.Description: Complete two missions in the Crypts Dungeon.

Quest:starlightquest_complete_d1_c.Name: StarlightQuest_Complete_D1_C
Quest:starlightquest_complete_d1_c.Description: Put all of your fears to an eternal rest and conquer The Crypts for good. Complete one final mission in the Crypts Dungeon.

Objectives.Description: Complete a mission in the Crypts Dungeon.
The Crypts Hard (Hidden)

Quest:starlightquest_complete_d2_a.Name: StarlightQuest_Complete_D2_A
Quest:starlightquest_complete_d2_a.Description: Inferno is a dungeon full of lava, fiery husks, and... fun! Complete a mission in the Inferno Dungeon to gain access to the Grotto!

Objectives.Description: Complete a mission in the Inferno Dungeon.

Quest:starlightquest_complete_d2_b.Name: StarlightQuest_Complete_D2_B
Quest:starlightquest_complete_d2_b.Description: The deeper you go into the Inferno Dungeon, the hotter it gets. Complete two missions in the Inferno Dungeon.

Objectives.Description: Complete two missions in the Inferno Dungeon.

Quest:starlightquest_complete_d2_c.Name: StarlightQuest_Complete_D2_C
Quest:starlightquest_complete_d2_c.Description: Complete one final mission in the Inferno Dungeon.

Objectives.Description: Complete a mission in the Inferno Dungeon.
Inferno Hard (Hidden)

Quest:starlightquest_complete_d3_a.Name: StarlightQuest_Complete_D3_A
Quest:starlightquest_complete_d3_a.Description: Complete a mission in the Grotto Dungeon to gain access to The Labyrinth.

Objectives.Description: Complete a mission in the Grotto Dungeon.

Quest:starlightquest_complete_d3_b.Name: StarlightQuest_Complete_D3_B
Quest:starlightquest_complete_d3_b.Description: Take a dip in The Grotto to clear out more husks! Complete two more missions in the Grotto Dungeon.

Objectives.Description: Complete two missions in the Grotto Dungeon.

Quest:starlightquest_complete_d3_c.Name: StarlightQuest_Complete_D3_C
Quest:starlightquest_complete_d3_c.Description: Complete one final mission in the Grotto Dungeon.

Objectives.Description: Complete a mission in the Grotto Dungeon.
The Grotto Hard (Hidden)

Quest:starlightquest_complete_d4_a.Name: StarlightQuest_Complete_D4_A
Quest:starlightquest_complete_d4_a.Description: Don’t lose yourself in the grand halls of The Labyrinth. Complete a mission in the Labyrinth Dungeon.

Objectives.Description: Complete a mission in the Labyrinth Dungeon.

Quest:starlightquest_complete_d4_b.Name: StarlightQuest_Complete_D4_B
Quest:starlightquest_complete_d4_b.Description: This Labyrinth seems to be changing every time we enter it… And, are we going in circles? Complete two more missions in the Labyrinth Dungeon.

Objectives.Description: Complete two missions in the Labyrinth Dungeon.

Quest:starlightquest_complete_d4_c.Name: StarlightQuest_Complete_D4_C
Quest:starlightquest_complete_d4_c.Description: Master The Labyrinth! Complete one final mission in the Labyrinth Dungeon.

Objectives.Description: Complete a mission in the Labyrinth Dungeon.
The Labyrinth Hard (Hidden)

Quest:starlightquest_complete_d5science_.Name: StarlightQuest_Complete_D5Science_A
Quest:starlightquest_complete_d5science_.Description: The Lab has been discovered! Enter if you dare! Complete a mission in the Lab Dungeon!

Objectives.Description: Complete a mission in the Lab Dungeon.

Quest:starlightquest_complete_d5science_.Name: StarlightQuest_Complete_D5Science_B
Quest:starlightquest_complete_d5science_.Description: The Lab is a perilous place, but you're not afraid! Complete two more missions in the Lab Dungeon.

Objectives.Description: Complete two missions in the Lab Dungeon.

Quest:starlightquest_complete_d5science_.Name: StarlightQuest_Complete_D5Science_C
Quest:starlightquest_complete_d5science_.Description: Complete one final mission in the Lab Dungeon.

Objectives.Description: Complete a mission in the Lab Dungeon.

Quest:starlightquest_complete_d5science_.Name: StarlightQuest_Complete_D5Science_Hard
Quest:starlightquest_complete_d5science_.Description: Complete the Lab at the most challenging level.

Objectives.Description: Complete the Lab Dungeon in a 140+ zone.

Quest:starlightquest_complete_dailies_1.Name: StarlightQuest_Complete_Dailies_1
Quest:starlightquest_complete_dailies_1.Description: A dungeon a day keeps the Husks at bay... Successfully complete 3 Daily Dungeon quests and start your quest to become a Daily Dungeon Destroyer!

Objectives.Description: Complete 3 Daily Dungeon quests.

Quest:starlightquest_complete_dailies_2.Name: StarlightQuest_Complete_Dailies_2
Quest:starlightquest_complete_dailies_2.Description: Dungeon clearing is a major part of a balanced daily nutritional plan. Successfully complete 6 total Daily Dungeon quests and further your quest to become a Daily Dungeon Destroyer!

Objectives.Description: Complete 6 Daily Dungeon quests.

Quest:starlightquest_complete_dailies_3.Name: StarlightQuest_Complete_Dailies_3
Quest:starlightquest_complete_dailies_3.Description: The final test of your dedication to Dungeon destruction! Successfully complete 10 total Daily Dungeon quests to finally become a Daily Dungeon Destroyer!

Objectives.Description: Complete 10 Daily Dungeon quests.

Quest:starlightquest_complete_melee_d1.Name: StarlightQuest_Complete_Melee_D1
Quest:starlightquest_complete_melee_d1.Description: A special Melee Only challenge is available in The Crypts! Complete this challenge to unlock a new Timed Run challenge.

Objectives.Description: Complete the Melee Only challenge in The Crypts.

Quest:starlightquest_complete_melee_time.Name: StarlightQuest_Complete_Melee_Timed_D1
Quest:starlightquest_complete_melee_time.Description: Complete the Melee Only Timed Run challenge for The Crypts!

Objectives.Description: Complete the Melee Only, Timed Run challenge in The Crypts.
Objectives.HudShortDescription: Melee Only / Timed Run Crypts completed

Quest:starlightquest_complete_timed_d1.Name: StarlightQuest_Complete_Timed_D1
Quest:starlightquest_complete_timed_d1.Description: Complete The Crypts within the allotted time or face certain doom! Completing this challenge will unlock a Timed Run challenge for Inferno.

Objectives.Description: Complete the Timed Run challenge in The Crypts.

Quest:starlightquest_complete_timed_d2.Name: StarlightQuest_Complete_Timed_D2
Quest:starlightquest_complete_timed_d2.Description: Complete Inferno within the allotted time or face certain doom! Completing this challenge will unlock a Timed Run challenge for The Grotto.

Objectives.Description: Complete the Timed Run challenge in Inferno.

Quest:starlightquest_complete_timed_d3.Name: StarlightQuest_Complete_Timed_D3
Quest:starlightquest_complete_timed_d3.Description: Complete The Grotto within the allotted time or face certain doom! Completing this challenge will unlock a Timed Run challenge for The Labyrinth.

Objectives.Description: Complete the Timed Run challenge in The Grotto.

Quest:starlightquest_complete_timed_d4.Name: StarlightQuest_Complete_Timed_D4
Quest:starlightquest_complete_timed_d4.Description: Complete The Labyrinth within the allotted time or face certain doom! Completing this challenge will unlock a special Melee Only Timed Run challenge for The Crypts.

Objectives.Description: Complete the Timed Run challenge in The Labyrinth.

Quest:starlightquest_daily_complete_d1.Name: StarlightQuest_Daily_Complete_D1
Quest:starlightquest_daily_complete_d1.Description:
Pay your respects to an old friend and successfully complete a mission in the Crypts Dungeon.
Note: This is a daily quest.

Objectives.Description: Complete a mission in the Crypts Dungeon.

Quest:starlightquest_daily_complete_d2.Name: StarlightQuest_Daily_Complete_D2
Quest:starlightquest_daily_complete_d2.Description:
Complete a mission in the Inferno Dungeon.
Note: This is a daily quest.

Objectives.Description: Complete a mission in the Inferno Dungeon.

Quest:starlightquest_daily_complete_d3.Name: StarlightQuest_Daily_Complete_D3
Quest:starlightquest_daily_complete_d3.Description:
Complete a mission in the Grotto Dungeon.
Note: This is a daily quest.

Objectives.Description: Complete a mission in the Grotto Dungeon.

Quest:starlightquest_daily_complete_d4.Name: StarlightQuest_Daily_Complete_D4
Quest:starlightquest_daily_complete_d4.Description:
Descend again into the Labyrinth! Complete a mission in the Labyrinth dungeon.
Note: This is a daily quest.

Objectives.Description: Complete a mission in the Labyrinth Dungeon.

Quest:starlightquest_daily_complete_d5sc.Name: StarlightQuest_Daily_Complete_D5Science
Quest:starlightquest_daily_complete_d5sc.Description:
Complete a mission in the Lab dungeon.
Note: This is a daily quest.

Objectives.Description: Complete a mission in the Lab Dungeon.

Quest:starlightquest_destroy_urns.Name: StarlightQuest_Destroy_Urns
Quest:starlightquest_destroy_urns.Description:
Smash as many spooky urns as you can in successful missions in the Dungeons. There’s gotta be valuables hidden within them!
Note: This is a repeatable quest.

Objectives.Description: Destroy 100 urns in successful Dungeon missions.

Quest:starlightquest_destructiblespawner.Name: StarlightQuest_DestructibleSpawners
Quest:starlightquest_destructiblespawner.Description: Husks are emerging from odd crystalline objects in the Dungeons. Destroy many of these in successful Dungeon missions to stop the onslaught.

Objectives.Description: Destroy 6 Husk Monoliths in successful Dungeon missions.

Quest:starlightquest_dungeoneer_construc.Name: StarlightQuest_Dungeoneer_Constructor
Quest:starlightquest_dungeoneer_construc.Description: Complete any Dungeon as a Constructor.

Objectives.Description: As a Constructor, successfully clear a Dungeon.

Quest:starlightquest_dungeoneer_ninja.Name: StarlightQuest_Dungeoneer_Ninja
Quest:starlightquest_dungeoneer_ninja.Description: Complete any Dungeon as a Ninja.

Objectives.Description: As a Ninja, successfully clear a Dungeon.

Quest:starlightquest_dungeoneer_outlande.Name: StarlightQuest_Dungeoneer_Outlander
Quest:starlightquest_dungeoneer_outlande.Description: Complete any Dungeon as an Outlander.

Objectives.Description: As an Outlander, successfully clear a Dungeon.

Quest:starlightquest_dungeoneer_soldier.Name: StarlightQuest_Dungeoneer_Soldier
Quest:starlightquest_dungeoneer_soldier.Description: Complete any Dungeon as a Soldier.

Objectives.Description: As a Soldier, successfully clear a Dungeon.

Quest:starlightquest_finitespawners.Name: StarlightQuest_FiniteSpawners
Quest:starlightquest_finitespawners.Description: Storm Rifts are appearing in the Dungeons and Husks are popping out in swarms! Eliminate Husks to deplete the rifts in successful Dungeon missions.

Objectives.Description: Deplete 6 Dungeon Rifts in successful Dungeon missions.

Quest:starlightquest_hidden_complete_d1_.Name: StarlightQuest_Hidden_Complete_D1_A
Quest:starlightquest_hidden_complete_d1_.Description: This quest will only be granted to players during the Fortnitemares 2021 season. The reason is the new Lab dungeon is shipping after this season has started, so we need a way to grant the first Lab quest if players have already completed the first Crypts dungeon quest. In subsequent Dungeon seasons, this quest will no longer be necessary since the Crypts quest will grant the first Lab quest as a quest reward.

Objectives.Description: (Hidden) Complete first Crypts quest.

Quest:starlightquest_kill_mimics.Name: StarlightQuest_Kill_Mimics
Quest:starlightquest_kill_mimics.Description: There is a ton of treasure to find in the Dungeons! But, it looks like not all of it is willing to go peacefully. Eliminate Mimics in successful Dungeon missions.

Objectives.Description: Eliminate 5 Mimics in successful Dungeon missions.

Quest:starlightquest_kill_minibosses.Name: StarlightQuest_Kill_Minibosses
Quest:starlightquest_kill_minibosses.Description:
Eliminate powerful Mini-Bosses in successful Dungeon missions. Doctors say "exorcising" is important for your health!
Note: This is a repeatable quest.

Objectives.Description: Eliminate 5 Mini-Bosses in successful Dungeon missions.

Quest:starlightquest_traptrial.Name: StarlightQuest_TrapTrial
Quest:starlightquest_traptrial.Description: Looks like some evil force acting against you has set up traps that can be seen with spooky glyphs. Become affected by each one of these new traps, for science!

Objectives.Description: Get hit by an Arrow Dungeon Trap.
Get snared by a Snare Dungeon Trap.
Get hit by a Ceiling Drop Dungeon Trap.
Get teleported by a Teleport Dungeon Trap.

Quest:stonewoodquest_ability_hoverboard.Name: StonewoodQuest_Ability_Hoverboard
Quest:stonewoodquest_ability_hoverboard.Description: It's time to hover! Hold down the (build/combat) mode switch button to activate your Hoverboard.

Objectives.Description: Ride your Hoverboard
Complete a mission in a 9+ zone
Complete a Fight the Storm mission

Quest:stonewoodquest_fetch_directorstuff.Name: StonewoodQuest_Fetch_DirectorStuff
Quest:stonewoodquest_fetch_directorstuff.Description: Ray needs help with managing survivors. The Director needs some tools. Search boxes and see what you can retrieve.

Objectives.Description: Search Boxes in a 15+ City, Suburban, or Industrial zone

Quest:stonewoodquest_fetch_researchcrate.Name: StonewoodQuest_Fetch_ResearchCrates
Quest:stonewoodquest_fetch_researchcrate.Description: Lars offers to setup a research lab at homebase. There was some equipment he ordered just before the storm, that never got delivered. We need to retrieve the shipments. This quest can be completed in the City, Suburban and Industrial zones.

Objectives.Description: Collect Research Equipment in a 5+ City, Suburban, or Industrial zone

Quest:stonewoodquest_fetch_stormcalls.Name: StonewoodQuest_Fetch_StormCalls
Quest:stonewoodquest_fetch_stormcalls.Description: We are receiving disturbing transmissions from Dennis. Retrieve these distress transmissions.

Objectives.Description: Collect Distress Transmissions in a 9+ City, Suburban, or Industrial zone

Quest:stonewoodquest_fetch_trashcans.Name: StonewoodQuest_Fetch_TrashCans
Quest:stonewoodquest_fetch_trashcans.Description: Everyone at Homebase is getting robbed. Search garbage cans in the zone to identify the culprit.

Objectives.Description: Search Garbage Cans for lost items in a 9+ City, Suburban, or Industrial zone

Quest:stonewoodquest_fetch_triangulating.Name: StonewoodQuest_Fetch_TriangulatingPop
Quest:stonewoodquest_fetch_triangulating.Description: We need to triangulate Pop's position. See what you can do, Commander!  Try Industrial or Urban Zones!

Objectives.Description: Deploy Scanners in a 15+ zone

Quest:stonewoodquest_filler_1_d2.Name: StonewoodQuest_Filler_1_D2
Quest:stonewoodquest_filler_1_d2.Description: Survivors are in need of rescue! Complete a mission and bring them home.

Objectives.Description: Save 3 Survivors in successful missions
Complete a mission in a 3+ zone

Quest:stonewoodquest_filler_1_d3.Name: StonewoodQuest_Filler_1_D3
Quest:stonewoodquest_filler_1_d3.Description: Survivors are in danger. Complete a Rescue the Survivors mission.

Objectives.Description: Complete a Rescue the Survivors mission in a 5+ zone

Quest:stonewoodquest_filler_1_d4.Name: StonewoodQuest_Filler_1_D4
Quest:stonewoodquest_filler_1_d4.Description: The husks have done us wrong, let's go do 'em in. Clear husk encampments and search for more.

Objectives.Description: Clear 4 Husk Encampments in successful missions in a 9+ zone
Complete 2 missions in a 9+ zone

Quest:stonewoodquest_filler_2_d4.Name: StonewoodQuest_Filler_2_D4
Quest:stonewoodquest_filler_2_d4.Description: Stock up on healing! Craft 5 Healing Pads, and complete 2 missions.

Objectives.Description: Craft Healing Pads
Complete 2 missions in a 5+ zone

Quest:stonewoodquest_filler_2_d5.Name: StonewoodQuest_Filler_2_D5
Quest:stonewoodquest_filler_2_d5.Description: Smashers and Takers are on the rampage. Defeat those Mist Monsters!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate 5 Mist Monsters in successful missions in a 15+ zone
Complete 3 missions in a 15+ zone

Quest:stonewoodquest_gathercollect_armor.Name: StonewoodQuest_GatherCollect_ArmoryUpgrade
Quest:stonewoodquest_gathercollect_armor.Description: The armory needs an upgrade. Gather machine parts by destroying industrial machinery to upgrade the manufacturing and modding capacity of the armory.

Objectives.Description: Collect Machine Parts in a 15+ Industrial zone
(Hidden) Collect 50 Items

Quest:stonewoodquest_joelkarolina_killhu.Name: StonewoodQuest_JoelKarolina_KillHusks
Quest:stonewoodquest_joelkarolina_killhu.Description: Take out those husks! Take them all down!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate Husks in successful missions in a 40+ zone

Quest:stonewoodquest_joelkarolina_killmi.Name: StonewoodQuest_JoelKarolina_KillMistMonsters
Quest:stonewoodquest_joelkarolina_killmi.Description: Let’s see what you can do against the mist monsters!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate Mist Monsters in successful missions in a 40+ zone

Quest:stonewoodquest_joelkarolina_savesu.Name: StonewoodQuest_JoelKarolina_SaveSurvivors
Quest:stonewoodquest_joelkarolina_savesu.Description: Survivors are in need of rescue! Save as many as you can!

Objectives.Description: Save Survivors in successful missions

Quest:stonewoodquest_killcollect_mistmon.Name: StonewoodQuest_KillCollect_MistMonsters
Quest:stonewoodquest_killcollect_mistmon.Description: Gather as much data as you can from the Mist Monsters to prepare for a showdown with the Storm King.

Objectives.Description: Collect Mist Monster data in a 15+ zone

Quest:stonewoodquest_landmark_buildoff.Name: StonewoodQuest_Landmark_BuildOff
Quest:stonewoodquest_landmark_buildoff.Description: It's a build off between Kyle and Penny! Complete a Constructor Build Off mission.

Objectives.Description: Complete the Constructor Build Off mission

Quest:stonewoodquest_launchballoon_d1.Name: StonewoodQuest_LaunchBalloon_D1
Quest:stonewoodquest_launchballoon_d1.Description: Meet freelance storm analyst / potentially dangerous weirdo, Lars.

Objectives.Description: Complete a Ride the Lightning mission

Quest:stonewoodquest_launchrocket_d5.Name: StonewoodQuest_LaunchRocket_D5
Quest:stonewoodquest_launchrocket_d5.Description: We've got blue skies and a rocket that's almost ready to fly. Get out there and launch your next Storm Shield.

Objectives.Description: Complete a Launch the Rocket mission in a 15+ zone

Quest:stonewoodquest_mechanical_buildlev.Name: StonewoodQuest_Mechanical_BuildLev2
Quest:stonewoodquest_mechanical_buildlev.Description: Kyle and Penny's final build off! Let's build some more structures!

Objectives.Description: Build Level 2 Structures in successful missions in a 9+ zone

Quest:stonewoodquest_mechanical_killhusk.Name: StonewoodQuest_Mechanical_KillHusks
Quest:stonewoodquest_mechanical_killhusk.Description: It's time to teach our defender trainee how to fight. Take on those husks!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate Husks with Melee Weapons in successful missions in a 15+ zone in Stonewood
Eliminate Husks with Ranged Weapons in successful missions in a 15+ zone in Stonewood
Eliminate Husks with Traps in successful missions in a 15+ zone in Stonewood

Quest:stonewoodquest_reactive_fetch_hove.Name: StonewoodQuest_Reactive_Fetch_Hoverboard
Quest:stonewoodquest_reactive_fetch_hove.Description: I just realized you don't have a Hoverboard! Let's fix that. Destroy Hot Rods to collect everything we'll need to build a Hoverboard.

Objectives.Description: Search City Zones for Hot Rods in successful missions in a 9+ zone

Quest:stonewoodquest_reactive_joelkaroli.Name: StonewoodQuest_Reactive_JoelKarolina_GatherPortraits
Quest:stonewoodquest_reactive_joelkaroli.Description: Look for portraits of Karolina while ridding the world of husks and monsters. Most often found in the attics of old houses.

Objectives.Description: Gather Portraits of Karolina in a 40+ zone

Quest:stonewoodquest_reactive_joelkaroli.Name: StonewoodQuest_Reactive_JoelKarolina_VisitPubs
Quest:stonewoodquest_reactive_joelkaroli.Description: Time to enjoy some downtime. Visit Joel's pubs while completing some missions.

Objectives.Description: Become a regular at Joel's Pub by visiting it on two occasions in a 40+ zone. Found in City zones.

Quest:stonewoodquest_retrievedata_d1.Name: StonewoodQuest_RetrieveData_D1
Quest:stonewoodquest_retrievedata_d1.Description: A research balloon is heading for hostile territory. Save the balloon and recover the intel.

Objectives.Description: Complete a Retrieve the Data mission

Quest:stonewoodquest_side_1_d3.Name: StonewoodQuest_Side_1_D3
Quest:stonewoodquest_side_1_d3.Description: Whack some Trolls and reclaim that BluGlo!

Objectives.Description: Whack 2 Trolls in successful missions in a 5+ zone

Quest:stonewoodquest_side_1_d4.Name: StonewoodQuest_Side_1_D4
Quest:stonewoodquest_side_1_d4.Description:
It's time to join up with other Commanders and complete a mission in Stonewood!

This Quest must be completed in Stonewood.

Objectives.Description: Complete 2 Play with Others missions in Stonewood

Quest:stonewoodquest_side_1_d5.Name: StonewoodQuest_Side_1_D5
Quest:stonewoodquest_side_1_d5.Description: If you can't handle Stonewood at its worst, you don't deserve those 15 survivors...

Objectives.Description: Save 15 Survivors in successful missions
Complete 3 missions in a 15+ zone

Quest:stonewoodquest_treasuredfriends.Name: StonewoodQuest_TreasuredFriends
Quest:stonewoodquest_treasuredfriends.Description: Go on a treasure hunt to stock up on weapons, ammo, traps, and crafting resources. Quest progress is shared with the group.

Objectives.Description: Loot a Treasure Chest in a successful mission in a 3+ zone

Quest:stormking_checkemail.Name: StormKing_CheckEmail
Quest:stormking_checkemail.Description: Congratulations! You have defeated the Storm King! Check your email over the next several days for information on getting a physical Storm King Pin!

Objectives.Description: (Hidden) Check Email

Quest:stormking_daily_landmark_bossfight.Name: StormKing_Daily_Landmark_Bossfight
Quest:stormking_daily_landmark_bossfight.Description: Defeat the Storm King! Are you up for this Daily Challenge?

Objectives.Description: Defeat the Storm King

Quest:stormking_hidden_hascompletedquest.Name: StormKing_Hidden_HasCompletedQuest
Quest:stormking_hidden_hascompletedquest.Description: (Hidden) Grants follow up quest to tell players to check email for more information on how to get their physical pin.

Objectives.Description: (Hidden) Complete Canny Valley Bossfight Quest

Quest:stormquest_2018_completestormzones.Name: StormQuest_2018_CompleteStormZones_Repeatable
Quest:stormquest_2018_completestormzones.Description: Storms are rapidly spreading. Look at all that purple turbulance on the map! Complete some missions in those hexes. Note: This is a repeatable Quest.

Objectives.Description: Complete 2 Mutant Storm missions

Quest:stormquest_2018_completesurvive7da.Name: StormQuest_2018_CompleteSurvive7Day_D1
Quest:stormquest_2018_completesurvive7da.Description:
Survive the Storm for 7 days in a Power 15 zone.

You can access Survive the Storm by selecting the Map tab and then selecting the Survive the Storm pin.

Objectives.Description: Complete a 7 Day Survive the Storm in a 15 zone

Quest:stormquest_2018_completesurvive7da.Name: StormQuest_2018_CompleteSurvive7Day_D2
Quest:stormquest_2018_completesurvive7da.Description:
Survive a 7 Day mission in a Power 40 zone.

You can access Survive the Storm by selecting the Map tab and then selecting the Survive the Storm pin.

Objectives.Description: Complete a 7 Day Survive the Storm in a 40 zone

Quest:stormquest_2018_completesurvive7da.Name: StormQuest_2018_CompleteSurvive7Day_D3
Quest:stormquest_2018_completesurvive7da.Description:
A 7 Day mission in a Power 70 zone? Can you survive?

You can access Survive the Storm by selecting the Map tab and then selecting the Survive the Storm pin.

Objectives.Description: Complete a 7 Day Survive the Storm in a 70 zone

Quest:stormquest_2018_completesurviveany.Name: StormQuest_2018_CompleteSurviveAny
Quest:stormquest_2018_completesurviveany.Description:
Successfully complete Survive the Storm missions in any threat level.

You can access Survive the Storm by selecting the Map tab and then selecting the Survive the Storm pin.

Objectives.Description: Complete 3 Survive the Storm missions
(Hidden) Complete StormQuest_2018_Reactive_SkyAtlases

Quest:stormquest_2018_hidden_watchvideo.Name: StormQuest_2018_Hidden_WatchVideo
Quest:stormquest_2018_hidden_watchvideo.DisplayName: (Hidden) Into the Storm Watch Video Quest

Objectives.Description: (Hidden) Watch Into the Storm Video

Quest:stormquest_2018_landmark_lars.Name: StormQuest_2018_Landmark_Lars
Quest:stormquest_2018_landmark_lars.Description: Launch Lars deep into the storm!

Objectives.Description: Launch Lars beyond the wall of clouds

Quest:stormquest_2018_landmark_observe.Name: StormQuest_2018_Landmark_Observe
Quest:stormquest_2018_landmark_observe.Description: It's time to finish Carlos' research! Protect the telescope array until the results come in!

Objectives.Description: Defend the telescope array (4 telescopes) while they are observing the sky

Quest:stormquest_2018_reactive_acparts.Name: StormQuest_2018_Reactive_ACParts
Quest:stormquest_2018_reactive_acparts.Description: Commander, I have come up with a foolproof hoverboard based plan to track Carlos down! The only problem is, these hoverboards are idiots! I need your help. Searching rooftops for AC units should help us find the parts we need. Found in Urban, Suburban and Industrial zones.

Objectives.Description: Gather AC control circuits from AC units for the Smart Hoverboards

Quest:stormquest_2018_reactive_equipment.Name: StormQuest_2018_Reactive_Equipment
Quest:stormquest_2018_reactive_equipment.Description: Lars has asked us not to search for Carlos. So let's play it cool... as we search the rooftops for Carlos' research equipment. Found mostly in Urban, Suburban and Industrial zones.

Objectives.Description: Find and interact with the research equipment someone's been installing on the rooftops

Quest:stormquest_2018_reactive_hoverboar.Name: StormQuest_2018_Reactive_Hoverboards
Quest:stormquest_2018_reactive_hoverboar.Description: We don't have time to train the hoverfleet, but I think they'll figure it out. Head out and launch those brilliant boards!

Objectives.Description: Deploy smart hoverboards on their journey

Quest:stormquest_2018_reactive_huskdata.Name: StormQuest_2018_Reactive_HuskData
Quest:stormquest_2018_reactive_huskdata.Description: We need husk data... the gross kind of husk data. So take no prisoners and collect all samples!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate and collect mist monster data

Quest:stormquest_2018_reactive_insulator.Name: StormQuest_2018_Reactive_Insulators
Quest:stormquest_2018_reactive_insulator.Description: Lars is not going to like it, but we need to upgrade his van for the journey into the storm.Gather the insulators from electrical transformers. Found mostly in Industrial zones.

Objectives.Description: Find insulators from power transformers around the world

Quest:stormquest_2018_reactive_maps.Name: StormQuest_2018_Reactive_Maps
Quest:stormquest_2018_reactive_maps.Description: If we're going to head out west, we'll need maps. Search the industrial zone for vehicles likely to have maps. Trucks are easiest to find in Industrial zones.

Objectives.Description: Gather maps from Trucks and RVs

Quest:stormquest_2018_reactive_payphones.Name: StormQuest_2018_Reactive_Payphones
Quest:stormquest_2018_reactive_payphones.Description: The Hover Fleet is calling back! Track down payphones to collect their reports. Found in Urban, Suburban and Industrial zones.

Objectives.Description: Find public payphones the smart hoverboards are calling and retrieve the data

Quest:stormquest_2018_reactive_records.Name: StormQuest_2018_Reactive_Records
Quest:stormquest_2018_reactive_records.Description: Steel Wool mania is sweeping Homebase. Scour the streets for anything Steel Wool related. Found mostly in Urban and Suburban zones.

Objectives.Description: Look for Steel Wool album records

Quest:stormquest_2018_reactive_research.Name: StormQuest_2018_Reactive_Research
Quest:stormquest_2018_reactive_research.Description: Lars' sensor upgrade is a success, but no one can understand the new data. The answer to this strange data may lie in Lars' past. Search any basements to find Lars' old research. Found in Urban, Suburban and Industrial zones.

Objectives.Description: Find Lars's old research data

Quest:stormquest_2018_reactive_servers.Name: StormQuest_2018_Reactive_Servers
Quest:stormquest_2018_reactive_servers.Description: Help Lars restore his van's systems by collecting backup data from any server racks you can find. Found mostly in Urban and Industrial zones.

Objectives.Description: Find server clusters in the world and use them for some number-crunching

Quest:stormquest_2018_reactive_serviceca.Name: StormQuest_2018_Reactive_ServiceCars
Quest:stormquest_2018_reactive_serviceca.Description: Lars' van can't keep up with the strange new developments in the sky. Blast open the Van's doors of perception by collecting encrypted radio components from emergency response vehicles.
