Objectives.Description: Destroy firetrucks, police cars and ambulances to retrieve Encrypted Radio parts

Quest:stormquest_2018_reactive_skyatlase.Name: StormQuest_2018_Reactive_SkyAtlases
Quest:stormquest_2018_reactive_skyatlase.Description: Lars hasn't slept in days and his vital signs do not look good. Let's check in to see what he needs before he crashes his van. The sky atlases can be found mostly in Urban and Suburban zones.

Objectives.Description: Find sky atlas parts by destroying bookshelves

Quest:stormquest_2018_reactive_speakers.Name: StormQuest_2018_Reactive_Speakers
Quest:stormquest_2018_reactive_speakers.Description: Lars is ready to rock. Who are we to stand in the way?

Objectives.Description: Deploy speakers and blast Steel Wool's greatest hits to repel the storm

Quest:stormquest_2018_reactive_telescope.Name: StormQuest_2018_Reactive_Telescopes
Quest:stormquest_2018_reactive_telescope.Description: Lars wants telescopes... I have no idea why. Search for telescope parts and I'll figure our what Lars is up to. Found in Urban, Suburban and Industrial zones.

Objectives.Description: Find broken telescopes that we could use to construct a telescope array

Quest:stwirwinintro_build_quest_a7.Name: STWIrwinIntro_Build_Quest_A7
Quest:stwirwinintro_build_quest_a7.Description: Distract the raptor forces with a perfectly built dino distraction.

Objectives.Description: Build a dino distraction

Quest:stwirwinintro_feed_quest_a2.Name: STWIrwinIntro_Feed_Quest_A2
Quest:stwirwinintro_feed_quest_a2.Description: Bribe Gia's wolf pack and other animals into spilling their secrets with tasty treats.

Objectives.Description: Feed the animals.

Quest:stwirwinintro_fetch_quest_a3.Name: STWIrwinIntro_Fetch_Quest_A3
Quest:stwirwinintro_fetch_quest_a3.Description: Help Ray and Gia bring peace to the wilds of Homebase with a no holds barred taming spree.

Objectives.Description: Tame Animals

Quest:stwirwinintro_fetch_quest_a5.Name: STWIrwinIntro_Fetch_Quest_A5
Quest:stwirwinintro_fetch_quest_a5.Description: Harness the searching skills the animal kingdom by joining a boar scavenger hunt.

Objectives.Description: Harness the boar's searching skills.

Quest:stwirwinintro_reactivekill_quest_a.Name: STWIrwinIntro_ReactiveKill_Quest_A1
Quest:stwirwinintro_reactivekill_quest_a.Description: Go on a wild game hunt to help Ray and Dennis take on the dangerous animal invasion.

Objectives.Description: Eliminate the wild animals.

Quest:stwirwinintro_reactivekill_quest_a.Name: STWIrwinIntro_ReactiveKill_Quest_A4
Quest:stwirwinintro_reactivekill_quest_a.Description: Eliminate wolfy confusion by teaching the pack to take out the husk horde.

Objectives.Description: Eliminate husks with a tamed wolf.

Quest:stwirwinintro_reactivekill_quest_a.Name: STWIrwinIntro_ReactiveKill_Quest_A6
Quest:stwirwinintro_reactivekill_quest_a.DisplayName: In the Hall of the Raptor Queen
Quest:stwirwinintro_reactivekill_quest_a.Description: Help the Raptor Queen cleanse her kingdom of mist monsters.

Objectives.Description: Eliminate Mist Monsters with a tamed raptor.

Quest:stwirwinraptor_quest_a01_hatching.Name: STWIrwinRaptor_Quest_A01_Hatching
Quest:stwirwinraptor_quest_a01_hatching.DisplayName: Don’t Bite the Hand that Tames
Quest:stwirwinraptor_quest_a01_hatching.Description: Show that you are the ultimate raptor wrangler by taming two raptors.

Objectives.Description: Tame 2 raptors

Quest:stwirwinraptor_quest_a03_riding.Name: STWIrwinRaptor_Quest_A03_Riding
Quest:stwirwinraptor_quest_a03_riding.Description: Prove you’re a real raptor riding pro by traveling 1000m on raptor-back.

Objectives.Description: Travel 1000m while riding a raptor

Quest:stwirwinraptor_quest_a04_eliminate.Name: STWIrwinRaptor_Quest_A04_Eliminate
Quest:stwirwinraptor_quest_a04_eliminate.Description: Eliminate 50 husks while riding any wildlife to prove your mounted combat skills!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate 50 husks while riding wildlife

Quest:stw_stormkinghard_firsttakedown.Name: STW_StormKingHard_FirstTakedown
Quest:stw_stormkinghard_firsttakedown.Description: They say the bigger they are, the harder they fall. We certainly hope that is the case with this new Storm King. Good luck, Commander!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate the Mythic Storm King

Quest:stw_stormkinghard_kingme.Name: STW_StormKingHard_KingMe
Quest:stw_stormkinghard_kingme.Description: The Storm King's minions are tough and should provide a great way to hone your skills. They are also blocking the way to the Storm King, so eliminating them is not really optional.

Objectives.Description: Eliminate 2 Epic Mini-Bosses in a 140+ zone

Quest:stw_stormkinghard_weekly_001.Name: STW_StormKingHard_Weekly_001
Quest:stw_stormkinghard_weekly_001.DisplayName: (Weekly) Scions of the Storm King: Mimics
Quest:stw_stormkinghard_weekly_001.Description: The Storm King's power grows! Hunt down mimics to slow him down.

Objectives.Description: Defeat 2 Mimics in Successful Missions in 140+ Zones

Quest:stw_stormkinghard_weekly_002.DisplayName: (Weekly) Scions of the Storm King: Storm Chests

Objectives.Description: Complete a Storm Chest in Successful Missions in 140+ Zones

Quest:stw_stormkinghard_weekly_003.Name: STW_StormKingHard_Weekly_003
Quest:stw_stormkinghard_weekly_003.DisplayName: (Weekly) Scions of the Storm King: Minibosses
Quest:stw_stormkinghard_weekly_003.Description: The Storm King's power grows! Defeat Minibosses to take out his support!

Objectives.Description: Defeat 3 Minibosses in Successful Missions in 140+ Zones

Quest:stw_stormkinghard_weekly_004.Name: STW_StormKingHard_Weekly_004

Objectives.Description: Eliminate 20 Mist Monsters in Successful Missions in 140+ Zones.

Quest:stw_stormkinghard_weekly_005.DisplayName: (Weekly) Scions of the Storm King: Survivors
Quest:stw_stormkinghard_weekly_005.Description: The Storm King's power grows! Save the Survivors affected before it's too late!

Objectives.Description: Rescue 10 Survivors in Successful Missions in 140+ Zones

Quest:stw_stormkinghard_weekly_006.Name: STW_StormKingHard_Weekly_006
Quest:stw_stormkinghard_weekly_006.DisplayName: (Weekly) Scions of the Storm King: Defend the Van
Quest:stw_stormkinghard_weekly_006.Description: The Storm King's power grows! We need to survey the Storm for changes!

Objectives.Description: Complete 3 Ride the Lightning missions in 140+ Zones

Quest:stw_stormkinghard_weekly_007.Name: STW_StormKingHard_Weekly_007

Quest:summerquest_2019_complete_all.Name: SummerQuest_2019_Complete_All

Quest:summerquest_2019_fetch_fireworks.Name: SummerQuest_2019_Fetch_Fireworks

Objectives.Description: Collect boxes of fireworks

Quest:summerquest_2019_fetch_flamingo.Name: SummerQuest_2019_Fetch_Flamingo
Quest:summerquest_2019_fetch_flamingo.Description: We're not going to make the slideshow of 10 Homebase Parties With Pizzaz if we don't have decorations!

Objectives.Description: Collect flamingo lawn ornaments

Quest:summerquest_2019_fetch_towels.Name: SummerQuest_2019_Fetch_Towels
Quest:summerquest_2019_fetch_towels.Description: There's a soggy emergency on the pool deck! Find towels! Hint: These are easiest found in city or surburban missions.

Objectives.Description: Collect pool towels

Quest:summerquest_2019_fetch_water.Description: What better way to celebrate the summer than hosting a party? Start it off right by getting something to drink for our guests...

Objectives.Description: Collect jugs of water

Quest:summerquest_2019_gather_air_condit.Name: SummerQuest_2019_Gather_Air_Conditioners
Quest:summerquest_2019_gather_air_condit.Description: The people of Homebase are officially too hot to party! Collect air conditioning parts to chill everyone out.

Objectives.Description: Harvest air conditioner units to collect their parts

Quest:summerquest_2019_harvest_basketbal.Name: SummerQuest_2019_Harvest_Basketball_Hoops
Quest:summerquest_2019_harvest_basketbal.Description: The Twine Bounders are set to take on the Plankerton Smashers in the first annual Homebase Playoffs... we should probably build a court. Collect basketball hoops.  Hint: These are easiest found in suburban missions.

Objectives.Description: Collect parts from basketball hoops

Quest:summerquest_2019_harvest_lawnmower.Name: SummerQuest_2019_Harvest_Lawnmower
Quest:summerquest_2019_harvest_lawnmower.Description: If the world has ended, why are we still mowing the lawn? Let’s destroy all remnants of that ancient chore and harvest their parts! Hint: These are easiest found in suburban missions.

Objectives.Description: Harvest lawn mower parts

Quest:summerquest_2019_kill_200.Name: SummerQuest_2019_Kill_200
Quest:summerquest_2019_kill_200.Description: We've got party crashers! Take 'em out!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate husks

Quest:summerquest_2019_kill_melee.Name: SummerQuest_2019_Kill_Melee
Quest:summerquest_2019_kill_melee.Description: Warm up for the 2nd annual Homebase Softball Extravaganza by taking a swing at some husks.

Objectives.Description: Eliminate husks with melee

Quest:summerquest_2019_kill_mist.Name: SummerQuest_2019_Kill_Mist
Quest:summerquest_2019_kill_mist.Description: We have reports of misty party crashers. Take 'em out!

Objectives.Description: Eliminate mist monsters of any type

Quest:summerquest_2019_kill_wargames.Name: SummerQuest_2019_Kill_Wargames
Quest:summerquest_2019_kill_wargames.Description: Nothing gets a party started like a fun ice breaker. Get the fun started with some Wargames. Access Wargames from the Storm Shield Computer in your Homebase or by assisting other players via Neighborhood Watch.

Objectives.Description: Complete two Wargames simulations

Quest:summerquest_2019_light_fireworks.Name: SummerQuest_2019_Light_Fireworks

Objectives.Description: Light off the fireworks

Objectives.Description: Rescue survivors

Objectives.Description: Destroy ice machines, freezers, or refrigerators to collect ice
